{"type":"message","id":"b92e0c9f","parentId":"ac10e904","timestamp":"2026-04-09T17:23:15.437Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6f711c0402b54f5c98026a55","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const express = require('express');\nconst { loadConfig } = require('./config');\nconst { TaskStore } = require('./persistence/TaskStore');\nconst { Scheduler } = require('./scheduler/Scheduler');\nconst { SandboxExecutor } = require('./executor/SandboxExecutor');\nconst { SecurityGateway } = require('./security/SecurityGateway');\nconst { createLogger } = require('./observability/logger');\nconst { HealthChecker } = require('./observability/health');\nconst { MetricsCollector } = require('./observability/metrics');\nconst { createApiRouter } = require('./router/api');\nconst { setupGracefulShutdown } = require('./utils/gracefulShutdown');\n\n(async () => {\n  // 1. 加载配置\n  const config = loadConfig();\n  const logger = createLogger(config);\n  logger.info('OpenClaw v8.0 starting...');\n\n  // 2. 初始化组件\n  const taskStore = new TaskStore(config);\n  await taskStore.init();\n  taskStore.on('error', (err) => logger.error({ err }, 'TaskStore error'));\n  taskStore.on('recovered', (count) => logger.info({ recovered: count }, 'Stale tasks recovered'));\n\n  const security = new SecurityGateway(config);\n  const executor = new SandboxExecutor(config, logger);\n  const metrics = new MetricsCollector();\n  const healthChecker = new HealthChecker(config, taskStore);\n\n  const scheduler = new Scheduler(taskStore, executor, config, logger);\n  scheduler.on('error', (err) => logger.error({ err }, 'Scheduler error'));\n  scheduler.on('task:started', ({ taskId }) => logger.info({ taskId }, 'Task started'));\n  scheduler.on('task:completed', ({ taskId }) => {\n    metrics.inc('tasks_completed');\n    logger.info({ taskId }, 'Task completed');\n  });\n  scheduler.on('task:failed', ({ taskId, error }) => {\n    metrics.inc('tasks_failed');\n    logger.warn({ taskId, error }, 'Task failed');\n  });\n  scheduler.on('draining', (count) => logger.info({ remaining: count }, 'Draining tasks'));\n\n  // 3. 启动调度器（不阻塞）\n  scheduler.start().catch(err => logger.fatal({ err }, 'Scheduler crashed'));\n\n  // 4. 创建 Express 应用\n  const app = express();\n  app.use(express.json({ limit: '10mb' }));\n  app.use((req, res, next) => {\n    logger.debug({ method: req.method, url: req.url }, 'Request');\n    next();\n  });\n\n  const apiRouter = createApiRouter(taskStore, scheduler, healthChecker, security, metrics, config);\n  app.use('/api', apiRouter);\n\n  // 5. 启动 HTTP 服务器\n  const server = app.listen(config.server.port, config.server.host, () => {\n    logger.info({ host: config.server.host, port: config.server.port }, 'OpenClaw v8.0 listening');\n  });\n\n  // 6. 优雅停机\n  setupGracefulShutdown(server, scheduler, taskStore, logger);\n})();\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775755395427}}
{"type":"message","id":"c89c80a8","parentId":"b92e0c9f","timestamp":"2026-04-09T17:23:54.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我理解了整体架构。让我分析用户提供的方案并给出预案。\n\n方案分析：\n1. Scene Classifier - 当前v8中没有scene-classifier目录，需要部署\n2. auto_improve - 在workspace中已有，需要通过skillLoader集成\n3. 完整集成 - 涉及修改SandboxExecutor\n\n我的预案应该：\n1. 评估当前缺失的组件\n2. 给出分步骤实施计划\n3. 识别潜在风险\n\n让我给用户一个清晰的预案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 方案分析\n\n### 当前状态\n\n| 组件 | 位置 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| v8 核心 | `~/.openclaw/v8/src/` | ✅ 完整 |\n| auto_improve | `workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/auto_improve/` | ✅ 已有 6 模块 |\n| scene-classifier | `v8/scene-classifier/` | ❌ 不存在 |\n| skillLoader | `v8/src/skills/` | ❌ 不存在 |\n\n---\n\n## 实施预案\n\n### 第一阶段：部署 scene-classifier（2 步）\n\n**Step 1.1** 创建目录 + 基础文件\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/{classifier,data,scripts,feedback,models,logs}\n```\n\n**Step 1.2** 部署 Python 服务（需要实现：\n- `app.py` - Flask 服务，端口 3103\n- `scene_classifier.py` - 嵌入分类器\n- `rule_classifier.py` - 规则兜底\n\n---\n\n### 第二阶段：集成 skillLoader（2 步）\n\n**Step 2.1** 创建 `src/skills/skillLoader.js`\n- 加载 `workspace/.../auto_improve/autoImprove.js`\n- 标准化 `execute(task, context)` 接口\n\n**Step 2.2** 修改 `SandboxExecutor.js`\n- 增加 `task.type === 'skill'` 分支\n- 调用 `loadSkill()` 而非 spawn\n\n---\n\n### 第三阶段：端到端测试（2 步）\n\n**Step 3.1** 启动服务 + 验证评分\n**Step 3.2** 提交技能任务 + 验证执行\n\n---\n\n## 风险评估\n\n| 风险 | 等级 | 缓解 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 分类器 Python 环境 | 中 | 使用 venv 隔离 |\n| auto_improve 路径依赖 | 低 | 通过 skillLoader 动态配置 |\n| 内存叠加 | 中 | 监控内存，建议 ≥4GB VPS |\n| 权限问题 | 低 | sandbox 已配置 uid/gid |\n\n---\n\n## 问题反馈\n\n1. **scene-classifier** 你是要从头创建还是从 workspace 的 `scene-classifier/` 复制？\n2. **auto_improve** 是直接复用现有 6 模块，还是需要调整？\n3. **优先级** 是否按上述三阶段顺序执行？\n\n请确认，我再具体实施。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5399,"output":617,"cacheRead":67456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73472,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775755395439,"responseId":"019d7344f32ab9de515214b06b96b94f"}}
