{"type":"message","id":"42b18cf0","parentId":"0dfcc936","timestamp":"2026-04-09T17:58:57.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到问题了！listener 的配置是调用 3102 的 `/api/intent` 和 `/api/score`，但这些端点在当前版本 2026.4.9 中可能已经不存在或者功能不同。我们需要把配置改为调用 3103 和 3104。让我更新配置。\n\n根据我们部署的服务：- 场景分类：3104 的 `/classify`\n- 评分：3103 的 `/api/score`\n\n但是 listener 代码调用的是 `/api/intent`（POST）和 `/api/score`（GET），这和我们部署的 API 格式不完全匹配。我需要检查 3102 上是否有这些端点。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7364f3ccc6971bccdd0c6b09c72d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"测试 3102 的接口...\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/intent -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\":\"test\"}' | head -c 100\necho \"\"\ncurl -s \"http://localhost:3102/api/score?task=test\" | head -c 100","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4465,"output":238,"cacheRead":108288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112991,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775757522113,"responseId":"019d7364ccdc46d62c25ef65f1722db1"}}
