{"type":"message","id":"b2ed46b8","parentId":"41f9a96d","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:03:59.394Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 02:03 GMT+8] 先评分，学习，给出预案再思考：# OpenClaw Listener 适配 v8 服务：完整实现\n\n## 一、总体设计原则\n\n- **低耦合**：通过环境变量配置服务地址，不硬编码。\n- **高鲁棒**：超时控制、熔断降级、优雅失败。\n- **格式兼容**：适配新旧响应格式差异，内部统一。\n- **可观测**：关键调用记录日志，便于排查。\n- **易维护**：独立模块，单一职责。\n\n---\n\n## 二、目标架构\n\n```\nListener (messageHandler.ts)\n │\n ├─→ ClassificationClient (调用 3104)\n │ └─ 降级：规则兜底\n │\n ├─→ ScoringClient (调用 3103)\n │ └─ 降级：默认评分\n │\n └─→ 原有业务逻辑（任务执行/回复生成）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、新增文件：`clients/v8Client.ts`\n\n在 Listener 项目中创建 `src/clients/v8Client.ts`，封装对分类和评分服务的调用。\n\n```typescript\n// src/clients/v8Client.ts\nimport axios, { AxiosError } from 'axios';\nimport { createLogger } from '../utils/logger';\n\nconst logger = createLogger('V8Client');\n\n// 环境变量配置\nconst CLASSIFIER_URL = process.env.CLASSIFIER_URL || 'http://localhost:3104/classify';\nconst SCORER_URL = process.env.SCORER_URL || 'http://localhost:3103/api/score';\nconst CLASSIFIER_TIMEOUT = parseInt(process.env.CLASSIFIER_TIMEOUT || '300');\nconst SCORER_TIMEOUT = parseInt(process.env.SCORER_TIMEOUT || '2000');\n\n// 熔断器状态（简化版，生产可用库如 opossum）\nlet circuitOpen = false;\nlet failureCount = 0;\nconst CIRCUIT_THRESHOLD = 3;\nconst CIRCUIT_RESET_TIMEOUT = 30000;\n\n// 定时重置熔断器\nsetInterval(() => {\n if (circuitOpen) {\n circuitOpen = false;\n failureCount = 0;\n logger.info('Circuit breaker reset');\n }\n}, CIRCUIT_RESET_TIMEOUT);\n\nexport interface ClassificationResult {\n isTask: boolean;\n confidence: number;\n scene: string; // 原始场景标签\n meta?: string;\n topCandidates?: Array<[string, number]>;\n source: 'classifier' | 'fallback';\n}\n\nexport interface ScoringResult {\n score: number;\n factors: Record<string, number>;\n recommendedStrategy: string;\n timeout: number;\n source: 'scorer' | 'fallback';\n}\n\n/**\n * 调用场景分类服务\n */\nexport async function classify(text: string): Promise<ClassificationResult> {\n if (circuitOpen) {\n logger.warn('Circuit breaker open, using fallback classification');\n return fallbackClassify(text);\n }\n\n try {\n const response = await axios.post(CLASSIFIER_URL, { text }, {\n timeout: CLASSIFIER_TIMEOUT,\n });\n\n const data = response.data;\n const scene = data.label || 'default';\n const isTask = isTaskScene(scene);\n\n logger.debug(`Classification: scene=${scene}, confidence=${data.confidence}, meta=${data.meta}`);\n\n // 重置失败计数\n failureCount = 0;\n\n return {\n isTask,\n confidence: data.confidence ?? 0.5,\n scene,\n meta: data.meta,\n topCandidates: data.top_candidates,\n source: 'classifier',\n };\n } catch (error) {\n failureCount++;\n logger.warn(`Classifier request failed (${failureCount}/${CIRCUIT_THRESHOLD}): ${getErrorMessage(error)}`);\n\n if (failureCount >= CIRCUIT_THRESHOLD) {\n circuitOpen = true;\n logger.error('Circuit breaker opened due to repeated failures');\n }\n\n return fallbackClassify(text);\n }\n}\n\n/**\n * 调用评分服务\n */\nexport async function score(prompt: string, context?: Record<string, any>): Promise<ScoringResult> {\n try {\n const response = await axios.post(SCORER_URL, { prompt, context }, {\n timeout: SCORER_TIMEOUT,\n });\n\n const data = response.data;\n logger.debug(`Scoring: score=${data.score}, strategy=${data.recommendedStrategy}`);\n\n return {\n score: data.score ?? 30,\n factors: data.factors ?? {},\n recommendedStrategy: data.recommendedStrategy ?? 'DIRECT',\n timeout: data.timeout ?? 60,\n source: 'scorer',\n };\n } catch (error) {\n logger.warn(`Scorer request failed: ${getErrorMessage(error)}`);\n return fallbackScore(prompt);\n }\n}\n\n// ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// 内部辅助函数\n// ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n/**\n * 判断场景是否属于任务类型\n */\nfunction isTaskScene(scene: string): boolean {\n const taskScenes = [\n 'task_multi_step',\n 'high_risk_automated',\n 'fault_recovery',\n 'task_status_query',\n 'cancel_task',\n ];\n return taskScenes.includes(scene);\n}\n\n/**\n * 降级分类：基于关键词的简单规则\n */\nfunction fallbackClassify(text: string): ClassificationResult {\n const lower = text.toLowerCase();\n const taskPatterns = [\n /运行|执行|构建|测试|部署|编译|安装|创建|删除|修改|重构|分析|检查|修复/,\n /帮我|请|做|写|生成|优化/,\n ];\n const isTask = taskPatterns.some(p => p.test(lower));\n\n let scene = 'default';\n if (/天气|你好|谢谢|笑话/.test(lower)) scene = 'chitchat';\n else if (/起不来|挂了|报错|失败|恢复/.test(lower)) scene = 'fault_recovery';\n else if (/重构|分析.*代码|优化/.test(lower)) scene = 'task_multi_step';\n else if (isTask) scene = 'task_multi_step';\n\n logger.debug(`Fallback classification: scene=${scene}, isTask=${isTask}`);\n\n return {\n isTask,\n confidence: 0.6,\n scene,\n source: 'fallback',\n };\n}\n\n/**\n * 降级评分：保守默认值\n */\nfunction fallbackScore(prompt: string): ScoringResult {\n // 简单启发：包含“重构/编译”等词给稍高评分\n const lower = prompt.toLowerCase();\n let score = 30;\n let strategy = 'DIRECT';\n let timeout = 60;\n\n if (/重构|编译|构建|测试|部署/.test(lower)) {\n score = 45;\n strategy = 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT';\n timeout = 180;\n }\n if (/monorepo|微服务|全栈/.test(lower)) {\n score = 70;\n strategy = 'PARALLEL_SHARDS';\n timeout = 300;\n }\n\n logger.debug(`Fallback scoring: score=${score}, strategy=${strategy}`);\n\n return {\n score,\n factors: {},\n recommendedStrategy: strategy,\n timeout,\n source: 'fallback',\n };\n}\n\nfunction getErrorMessage(error: unknown): string {\n if (axios.isAxiosError(error)) {\n return error.message;\n }\n return String(error);\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、修改 `messageHandler.ts`\n\n在原有消息处理逻辑中，将调用旧 Gateway 的部分替换为使用上述客户端。\n\n### 4.1 定位原调用代码\n\n原代码可能类似：\n\n```typescript\n// 原有调用\nconst intentRes = await axios.post('http://localhost:3102/api/intent', { text: message });\nconst isTask = intentRes.data.isTask;\n\nif (isTask) {\n const scoreRes = await axios.post('http://localhost:3102/api/score', { prompt: message });\n // ...\n}\n```\n\n### 4.2 替换为新客户端\n\n```typescript\n// messageHandler.ts 修改片段\nimport { classify, score, ClassificationResult, ScoringResult } from '../clients/v8Client';\n\nasync function processMessage(userMessage: string, context: any) {\n // 1. 场景分类（带降级）\n const classification: ClassificationResult = await classify(userMessage);\n\n // 2. 根据场景决定后续\n if (!classification.isTask) {\n // 非任务：直接生成回复（使用模板或 LLM）\n return handleNonTask(userMessage, classification);\n }\n\n // 3. 任务类型：调用评分服务\n const scoring: ScoringResult = await score(userMessage, {\n // 可传入额外上下文，如文件数量等\n ...context,\n });\n\n // 4. 根据策略执行\n if (scoring.recommendedStrategy === 'DIRECT') {\n // 直接执行命令\n return executeDirectly(userMessage, scoring.timeout);\n } else {\n // 提交到 v8 任务编排器\n const taskId = await submitV8Task(userMessage, scoring);\n return {\n reply: `任务已提交 (ID: ${taskId})，预计 ${scoring.timeout} 秒完成。可通过 /task ${taskId} 查询状态。`,\n };\n }\n}\n\n/**\n * 处理非任务场景\n */\nfunction handleNonTask(message: string, classification: ClassificationResult) {\n switch (classification.scene) {\n case 'chitchat':\n return { reply: '你好！有什么技术问题需要帮助？' };\n case 'fault_recovery':\n return {\n reply: '请描述具体的故障现象和已尝试的操作，我将协助恢复。'\n };\n case 'vague_request':\n return {\n reply: '我不太确定你的具体需求。你可能想要：\\n1. 执行某个任务\\n2. 查询任务状态\\n3. 获取帮助信息\\n请具体说明。'\n };\n default:\n // 默认走 LLM 生成\n return generateLLMResponse(message);\n }\n}\n\n/**\n * 提交任务到 v8 编排器\n */\nasync function submitV8Task(userMessage: string, scoring: ScoringResult): Promise<string> {\n const response = await axios.post('http://localhost:3103/api/task', {\n type: 'command', // 或 'skill'，根据内容判断\n command: extractCommand(userMessage), // 需实现命令提取逻辑\n timeout: scoring.timeout,\n priority: calculatePriority(scoring.score),\n metadata: {\n prompt: userMessage,\n strategy: scoring.recommendedStrategy,\n },\n });\n return response.data.id;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、配置环境变量\n\n在 Listener 的 `.env` 文件中添加：\n\n```env\nCLASSIFIER_URL=http://localhost:3104/classify\nSCORER_URL=http://localhost:3103/api/score\nCLASSIFIER_TIMEOUT=300\nSCORER_TIMEOUT=2000\n```\n\n若使用其他配置方式，相应调整。\n\n---\n\n## 六、测试验证\n\n### 6.1 单元测试（可选）\n\n创建 `tests/v8Client.test.ts`：\n\n```typescript\nimport { classify, score } from '../src/clients/v8Client';\n\ndescribe('V8Client', () => {\n it('should classify a task message', async () => {\n const result = await classify('帮我分析代码');\n expect(result.isTask).toBe(true);\n expect(result.scene).toMatch(/task/);\n });\n\n it('should fallback when service unavailable', async () => {\n // 模拟服务不可用\n process.env.CLASSIFIER_URL = 'http://localhost:9999/classify';\n const result = await classify('test');\n expect(result.source).toBe('fallback');\n });\n});\n```\n\n### 6.2 集成测试\n\n启动分类和评分服务后，发送真实消息，观察日志：\n\n```bash\n# Listener 日志\ntail -f /home/ai/openclaw-listener/logs/app.log | grep -E \"Classification|Scoring\"\n```\n\n预期输出类似：\n```\nClassification: scene=task_multi_step, confidence=0.95, meta=confident\nScoring: score=33, strategy=STEP_ARCHIVE\n```\n\n### 6.3 故障模拟\n\n停止分类服务：\n```bash\npkill -f \"python app.py\"\n```\n\n再次发送消息，日志应显示降级行为：\n```\nClassifier request failed (1/3): timeout\n...\nFallback classification: scene=task_multi_step, isTask=true\n```\n\n---\n\n## 七、回滚计划\n\n若出现问题，可快速回退到旧 Gateway 调用：\n\n1. 恢复 `messageHandler.ts` 中原有调用逻辑（通过 Git 回退）。\n2. 重启 Listener。\n\n由于新旧逻辑完全解耦，回滚无副作用。\n\n---\n\n## 八、后续优化建议\n\n1. **熔断器增强**：使用 `opossum` 库提供更完善的熔断策略。\n2. **响应缓存**：对相同消息短期内缓存分类结果，减少重复调用。\n3. **指标采集**：记录调用延迟、成功率等，接入监控系统。\n4. **动态配置**：支持通过配置中心动态调整超时和阈值。\n\n---\n\n## 九、完整文件清单\n\n```\nopenclaw-listener/\n├── .env # 新增环境变量\n├── src/\n│ ├── clients/\n│ │ └── v8Client.ts # 新增：封装分类与评分调用\n│ ├── messageHandler.ts # 修改：替换原有调用\n│ └── utils/\n│ └── logger.ts # 假设已有\n└── tests/\n └── v8Client.test.ts # 可选\n```\n\n---\n\n以上方案经过多轮自我修正，考虑了：\n- **故障隔离**：超时、熔断、降级。\n- **格式兼容**：内部统一接口，屏蔽外部变化。\n- **可观测性**：关键路径日志。\n- **扩展性**：易于增加新的预处理步骤。"}],"timestamp":1775757839379}}
