{"type":"message","id":"4ca5a830","parentId":"9e04c889","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:12:32.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Session 是活跃的 (updated just now)，所以消息确实到达了。Gateway 应该会处理它。但是我的修改是在 Listener 里的 V8Client，而 WebChat 直接走 Gateway，没有走 Listener！所以分类和评分没有被调用。\n\n问题在于：当前的消息是从 WebChat 直接发送到 Gateway (3102)，不经过 openclaw-listener (3106)。\n\n需要在 Gateway 端添加分类和评分调用。让我看看 Gateway 的消息处理路径，或者让用户通过其他渠道（比如微信或飞书）发送消息，这些消息会经过 Listener。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n**问题发现**：你当前通过 **WebChat** 发送消息，直接走 Gateway，**不经过 Listener**。\n\n我修改的 v8Client 在 Listener 里，但 WebChat 消息路径是：\n```\nWebChat → Gateway (3102) → 直接处理\n```\n\n**而 Listener (3106)** 接收的是微信/飞书等其他渠道的消息。\n\n---\n\n**有两个选择**：\n\n1. **继续**：用微信/飞书发消息，会经过 Listener → 分类 → 评分\n2. **修改 Gateway**：在 Gateway 端也添加分类评分调用（需要额外工作）\n\n你想用哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1379,"output":235,"cacheRead":126720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128334,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775758332298,"responseId":"019d73713c99b114333dc23039c2421d"}}
