{"type":"message","id":"2ddeec38","parentId":"7dab8d7b","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:19:54.787Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 的代码在编译后的 dist 目录中，但我很难修改它。让我换一个思路：直接看一下当前 Gateway 的 WebChat 消息处理流程是怎样的。\n\n实际上，我应该先问用户：这个方案需要修改 Gateway 的源码，但 Gateway 可能是编译后的代码，不容易直接修改。\n\n让我给用户一个更实际的方案：也许可以创建一个中间件服务，或者直接在 workspace 的 skills 层面处理（这更符合 OpenClaw 的设计模式）。\n\n但用户发的这个方案确实需要修改 Gateway 代码。让我先确认 Gateway 的源码在哪里，然后按照方案实施。让我尝试另一种方法来找 Gateway 源码：\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7378c3c3dfd6d8f96243895cff95","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查看 gateway 进程的完整命令\ncat /proc/$(pgrep -f \"openclaw-gateway\" | head -1)/cmdline | tr '\\0' ' '\necho \"\"\n# 尝试找 dist 目录\nls -la ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/ | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":859,"output":218,"cacheRead":132224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133301,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775758781343,"responseId":"019d7378a27bb77730b105d03019502c"}}
