{"type":"message","id":"cd4f2155","parentId":"f8b90858","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:20:05.593Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 是编译后的代码，很难直接修改源码。但用户给了一个方案，我需要评估这个方案的可行性。让我给用户一个更实际的回复，说明 Gateway 源码位置的问题，并提供替代方案。\n\n实际上，有另一个更简单的方法：在 v8 的 api 路由里已经有一个 /api/score 接口，但 /chat/send 是在 Gateway 里的。\n\n让我思考一下最好的办法：\n1. 方案 A：创建一个新的服务作为 Gateway 的前置代理\n2. 方案 B：使用 OpenClaw 的 skill 机制（在 workspace 层处理）\n3. 方案 C：修改 Gateway 源码（需要找到源码）\n\n考虑到实际情况，我觉得方案 B 最简单 - 通过配置让 Gateway 调用 workspace 里的 skills。但用户给的方案是修改 Gateway 源码。\n\n让我给用户一个实际的回复，说明问题并提供建议。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 分析\n\nGateway 源码是编译后的（`dist/` 目录），无法直接修改。\n\n### 现有方案对比\n\n| 方案 | 说明 | 复杂度 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| **A** 修改 Gateway 源码 | 需找到源码并重新构建 | 高 |\n| **B** 创建前置代理 | 让 WebChat 走 3103/3104 | 中 |\n| **C** 用 Skills 机制 | 在 workspace 层处理 | 低 |\n\n---\n\n### 推荐方案 B：WebChat 走 v8 服务\n\n创建一个简单的代理服务，把 WebChat 请求转发到 v8：\n\n```\nWebChat → Proxy (3102新) → 3104分类 → 3103评分 → 执行\n```\n\n**但这样端口会冲突。**\n\n---\n\n### 最简方案：直接修改 Gateway 的 chat 路由\n\n让我检查 Gateway 是否支持插件或 hooks：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d93c8d98ac5b4f2aaa9f1edc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/hooks/ 2>/dev/null\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/*/hooks/ 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":133913,"output":403,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134316,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775758799183,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c06f0ef0-0482-451e-b585-59cfe9919ec7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"67572342","parentId":"cd4f2155","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:20:05.682Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d93c8d98ac5b4f2aaa9f1edc","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"HOOK.md\ncontext-hook.js\nhandler.js\nhandler.ts\non-command-error.sh\non-message.sh\nself-improvement.js"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":48,"aggregated":"HOOK.md\ncontext-hook.js\nhandler.js\nhandler.ts\non-command-error.sh\non-message.sh\nself-improvement.js","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775758805671}}
{"type":"message","id":"ccc04d2e","parentId":"67572342","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:20:13.601Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OpenClaw 有 hooks 机制！`on-message.sh` 可以用来在消息处理前执行操作。这可能是最简单的集成方式。\n\n让我看一下这个 hook 文件的内容：\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7379183d0838caa5e7a8db698c30","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/on-message.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":9188,"output":69,"cacheRead":125056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134313,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775758805686,"responseId":"019d73790229828342b98c35e34b238a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"221bb35f","parentId":"ccc04d2e","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:20:13.687Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d7379183d0838caa5e7a8db698c30","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Context Hook - HTTP 版本\n# 将消息发送到保护层的 HTTP 服务\n\nMESSAGE=\"${OPENCLAW_MESSAGE:-}\"\nUSER=\"${OPENCLAW_SENDER:-unknown}\"\nCHANNEL=\"${OPENCLAW_CHANNEL:-unknown}\"\nSERVER_URL=\"http://127.0.0.1:18790\"\n\nif [ -n \"$MESSAGE\" ]; then\n  # 发送到 HTTP 服务\n  curl -s -X POST \"${SERVER_URL}/api/context/add\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"role\\\":\\\"user\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"$(echo \"$MESSAGE\" | jq -Rs .)\\\",\\\"user\\\":\\\"$USER\\\",\\\"channel\\\":\\\"$CHANNEL\\\"}\" \\\n    > /dev/null 2>&1 || true\nfi"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775758813671}}
{"type":"message","id":"2181b8c1","parentId":"221bb35f","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:20:39.417Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OpenClaw 的 on-message.sh hook 可以用来在消息处理前执行操作！这是一个更好的集成点。我们可以：\n1. 在 on-message.sh 里调用 3104 分类和 3103 评分\n2. 分类和评分结果可以通过环境变量传递给后续处理\n\n但这需要修改 hook 脚本。让我给用户提供这个更简单的方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## ✅ 更好的方案：使用 OpenClaw Hooks\n\nOpenClaw 已有 `on-message.sh` 钩子，可以在消息进入前执行分类和评分。\n\n---\n\n### 实施方案\n\n修改 `~/.openclaw/hooks/on-message.sh`：\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\nMESSAGE=\"${OPENCLAW_MESSAGE:-}\"\nMESSAGE_FILE=\"/tmp/openclaw_last_msg.json\"\n\n# 分类 (3104)\nCLASSIFY_RESP=$(curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3104/classify \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d \"{\\\"text\\\": \\\"$MESSAGE\\\"}\" 2>/dev/null)\n\nSCENE=$(echo \"$CLASSIFY_RESP\" | grep -o '\"scene\":\"[^\"]*\"' | cut -d'\"' -f4)\nIS_TASK=$(echo \"$CLASSIFY_RESP\" | grep -o '\"isTask\":[^,}]*' | cut -d':' -f2)\n\n# 如果是任务，调用评分 (3103)\nif [ \"$IS_TASK\" = \"true\" ]; then\n  SCORE_RESP=$(curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3103/api/score \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"prompt\\\": \\\"$MESSAGE\\\"}\" 2>/dev/null)\n  \n  SCORE=$(echo \"$SCORE_RESP\" | grep -o '\"score\":[^,}]*' | cut -d':' -f2)\n  STRATEGY=$(echo \"$SCORE_RESP\" | grep -o '\"recommendedStrategy\":\"[^\"]*\"' | cut -d'\"' -f4)\n  \n  echo \"SCORE=$SCORE\" >> \"$MESSAGE_FILE\"\n  echo \"STRATEGY=$STRATEGY\" >> \"$MESSAGE_FILE\"\nfi\n\necho \"SCENE=$SCENE\" >> \"$MESSAGE_FILE\"\n```\n\n---\n\n**这个方案**：\n- ✅ 不需要改 Gateway 源码\n- ✅ 利用现有 hooks 机制\n- ✅ 消息进入前自动分类评分\n\n**要实施这个方案吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2784,"output":503,"cacheRead":131712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134999,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775758813693,"responseId":"019d7379263bfff0823c75aba54259ce"}}
