{"type":"message","id":"f60b0923","parentId":"9c4c9a16","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:32:38.883Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想了解 3105 和 3102 的区别。让我解释一下。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 3102 vs 3105\n\n| 对比 | 3102 | 3105 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **身份** | 原始 Gateway | v8 前置代理 |\n| **分类** | ❌ 无 | ✅ 调用 3104 |\n| **评分** | ❌ 无 | ✅ 调用 3103 |\n| **闲聊处理** | 直接 LLM | 返回快速模板（不调用 LLM） |\n| **任务处理** | 直接执行 | 评分后决定策略 |\n| **速度** | 慢（纯 LLM） | 快（闲聊直接返回） |\n| **复杂度** | 低 | 中 |\n\n### 简单说\n\n- **3102**：你发消息 → 直接给 LLM → 返回结果\n- **3105**：你发消息 → **先分类+评分** → 闲聊直接回，任务转发 Gateway → 返回结果\n\n你想试试 3105 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":142594,"output":215,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775759555161,"responseId":"chatcmpl-23671a71-4504-4054-a10e-62d0066dfb55"}}
