{"type":"message","id":"0beaadb3","parentId":"09f5cdd9","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:33:35.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"3105 是一个 API 代理服务，不是 Web 页面。它没有前端界面。我需要告诉用户这个是 API 接口，不是网页。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n**3105 是 API 服务，不是网页**。\n\n只能通过 curl 或 API 工具测试：\n\n```bash\n# 测试闲聊\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3105/api/chat/send \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\": \"你好\"}'\n\n# 测试任务\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3105/api/chat/send \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\": \"帮我分析代码\"}'\n```\n\n**如果你想用网页界面操作 OpenClaw，访问的是 Control UI**，那个是另外的地址。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":143002,"output":158,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143160,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775759613097,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8c501aca-eb5a-4696-a76e-80f03df5152b"}}
