{"type":"message","id":"0daddcb4","parentId":"f93d02c8","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:39:43.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问这些都有什么用，我来解释一下各个端口和功能的用途。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 功能说明\n\n| 端口 | 功能 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **3102** | 原始 Gateway | 基础对话（无分类评分） |\n| **3103** | v8 评分引擎 | 任务复杂度评分（内部用） |\n| **3104** | 场景分类器 | 识别意图类型（内部用） |\n| **3105** | v8 代理 | 智能聊天：闲聊直接回，任务评分后执行 |\n| **3110** | Control UI | 网页管理界面（目前认证有问题） |\n\n---\n\n## 推荐用法\n\n- **聊天**：用 **3105**，会先分类评分\n- **微信/飞书**：经过 Listener 自动调用 3104+3103\n- **管理**：用 **3110**（认证问题待解决）\n\n---\n\n你想要什么功能？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1703,"output":196,"cacheRead":145152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147051,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775759970497,"responseId":"019d738a0b8ed1c2200c8fb34f967de0"}}
