{"type":"message","id":"6823922c","parentId":"bbced244","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:40:51.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说 3105 也进不去，显示 Cannot GET /。这是因为 3105 是一个 API 代理服务，不是网页服务。它只有 /api/chat/send 端点，没有网页界面。\n\n3102、3105 都是 API 服务，不是网页。3110 是 Control UI 网页，但有认证问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**3105 是 API 服务，不是网页**。\n\n| 端口 | 类型 | 访问方式 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 3102 | API | curl/代码调用 |\n| 3105 | API | curl/代码调用 |\n| 3110 | **网页** | 浏览器（当前认证有问题） |\n\n---\n\n**目前没有可直接浏览的聊天界面**。\n\n你可以：\n1. **用 curl 测试 3105**：curl -X POST http://localhost:3105/api/chat/send -d '{\"message\":\"你好\"}'\n2. **解决 3110 认证**：我可以帮你修复\n\n要修 Control UI 认证吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":147248,"output":202,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147450,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775760048462,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7ee6fdfb-cab9-46cd-aed3-8cf591c02559"}}
