{"type":"message","id":"622e7918","parentId":"fc6f4fc0","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:44:46.377Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d738f8a0d36edfeb4fe0c7f4ede7a","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== gateway.auth ===\n  \"auth\": {\n    \"profiles\": {\n      \"openai:default\": {\n        \"provider\": \"openai\",\n        \"mode\": \"api_key\"\n      },\n--\n    \"auth\": {\n\n=== controlUi ===\n    \"controlUi\": {\n      \"allowInsecureAuth\": true,\n      \"enabled\": true\n    },"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":45,"aggregated":"=== gateway.auth ===\n  \"auth\": {\n    \"profiles\": {\n      \"openai:default\": {\n        \"provider\": \"openai\",\n        \"mode\": \"api_key\"\n      },\n--\n    \"auth\": {\n\n=== controlUi ===\n    \"controlUi\": {\n      \"allowInsecureAuth\": true,\n      \"enabled\": true\n    },","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775760286366}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce0e27e5","parentId":"622e7918","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:45:01.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"配置看起来正确 - `allowInsecureAuth: true` 已设置。问题是 URL 传 token 的方式可能不对。让我看看 Control UI 具体怎么验证。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d738f27c9f51d73ebbba086fb63d6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 尝试不同方式访问\necho \"=== 方式1: query 参数 ===\"\ncurl -s \"http://localhost:3110/?token=0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced\" | head -c 100\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 方式2: Header Authorization ===\"\ncurl -s -H \"Authorization: Bearer 0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced\" http://localhost:3110/ | head -c 100"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3308,"output":184,"cacheRead":145152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148644,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775760286385,"responseId":"019d738f10894b95f929b7a76dd24aea"}}
