{"type":"message","id":"a65c2095","parentId":"10751007","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:45:13.405Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用 Header Authorization 方式成功了！用户需要在浏览器里用这种方式访问，或者我应该告诉用户正确的访问方法。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## ✅ 有解决办法\n\n**用 Header 方式访问**（不是 URL token 参数）：\n\n在浏览器控制台执行：\n```javascript\n// 打开浏览器 F12 → Console，粘贴：\nlocalStorage.setItem('authToken', '0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced')\nlocation.reload()\n```\n\n或者直接用 curl 测试是可以的：\n```bash\ncurl -H \"Authorization: Bearer 0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced\" http://localhost:3110/\n```\n\n返回了 `{\"enabled\":true,\"profile\":\"openclaw\",...}`，证明认证成功。\n\n---\n\n**方案**：在浏览器设置 localStorage token 后刷新即可正常使用 Control UI。\n\n要试试吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":483,"output":199,"cacheRead":148224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148906,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775760301484,"responseId":"019d738fd36ecdffc32dd865222de677"}}
