{"type":"message","id":"2fd4f7fc","parentId":"c7bbd5cd","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:46:56.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问 3110 端口是什么。是的，3110 是 Control UI 的端口。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n是的，**3110 是 Control UI**。\n\n```bash\ncurl -H \"Authorization: Bearer 0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced\" http://localhost:3110/\n```\n\n成功返回了：`{\"enabled\":true,\"profile\":\"openclaw\",...}`\n\n浏览器打开方法：F12 → Console → 输入：\n```javascript\nlocalStorage.setItem('authToken', '0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced')\n```\n然后刷新页面。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5082,"output":148,"cacheRead":143744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148974,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775760404312,"responseId":"019d7390c7a2ca8d4346fdd8074b0875"}}
