{"type":"message","id":"ec304125","parentId":"e2bfd493","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:50:11.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要一个跟 3102 一样的聊天界面。3102 是 Gateway 的 API 端口，不是网页界面。可能用户误解了，以为 3102 有一个网页聊天界面可以浏览。\n\n实际上，3102/3105/3103/3104 都是 API 端口，不是网页。它们需要通过前端应用或 curl 来调用。\n\nOpenClaw 可能有另一个用于聊天的网页界面？让我检查一下是否有其他端口提供网页聊天功能。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7393ed5dba164faa78aa5a048e1f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查是否有其他端口提供网页界面\nss -tlnp | grep -E \"80|443|3000|8080|5000\"\necho \"---\"\n# 查看是否有 webchat 相关\ngrep -r \"webchat\\|chat.*ui\\|html\" ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3055,"output":185,"cacheRead":146560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":149800,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775760598061,"responseId":"019d7393d05f2b19be27e88288ad1595"}}
