{"type":"message","id":"20eee03c","parentId":"5e9ed7a3","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:51:15.555Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问什么意思，可能对我给出的信息感到困惑。让我简单解释一下他在做什么。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 简单说\n\n你现在跟我（OpenClaw）聊天，用的是 **WebChat**，它连接的是 **3102 端口**的 Gateway。\n\n**现在有两个入口**：\n\n| 端口 | 作用 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **3102** | Gateway（原始版） | ✅ 正在用 |\n| **3105** | Gateway + v8分类评分（新版） | ✅ 可用 |\n\n你之前测试的 `curl -X POST http://localhost:3105/api/chat/send -d '{\"message\":\"你好\"}'` 就是新版的测试。\n\n---\n\n**你现在的对话走的是 3102**（没有分类评分）。\n\n**要试试 3105 吗？** 但需要把 WebChat 客户端配置改成连接到 3105。\n\n你现在有客户端可以连接吗？还是用命令行测试？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":649,"output":194,"cacheRead":149504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":150347,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775760660747,"responseId":"019d739552048c11df8642cc1098611e"}}
