{"type":"message","id":"cfb9c02e","parentId":"00362e31","timestamp":"2026-04-09T18:57:57.773Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"bypass 模式下返回 \"Gateway unavailable\"。这很奇怪，因为我刚才直接测试 3102 是成功的。\n\n可能问题在于代理代码里的 axios 配置或超时。让我简化代理代码，或者检查 3102 实际监听的地址。\n\n实际上，3102 监听的是 `*:3102`（所有接口），而 3108 监听的是 127.0.0.1:3108。让我确认 3102 没问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fd26f2418f38476b9fdd140c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 3102 健康 ===\"\ncurl -s http://localhost:3102/health | head -c 100\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 3102 chat 直接 ===\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/chat/send -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\": \"测试\"}'","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":156180,"output":196,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156376,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775761073297,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3ffba31d-06ba-4bee-8d5e-4351be5a0ddd"}}
