{"type":"message","id":"2e04a76a","parentId":"886a43e8","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:03:40.043Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"根据用户提供的上下文，他的 WebChat 是通过 openclaw-control-ui 连接到 Gateway 的。那个 UI 是 3110 端口。但用户想要的是改变 WebChat 客户端连接地址从 3102 改成 3105。\n\n让我看看是否有一个 webchat 相关的配置或者客户端代码需要修改。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d73a01c5a1eba6eef570a6e81a99d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 webchat 相关的客户端配置\nls ~/.openclaw/ | grep -i web\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/ | grep -i web"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":6072,"output":116,"cacheRead":155648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":161836,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775761409638,"responseId":"019d739fff809f6201c1e02b8ab9119a"}}
