{"type":"message","id":"d59b7b2a","parentId":"a130841d","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:04:01.832Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，让我告诉用户：现在 Gateway (3102) 和 代理 (3105) 都可以用。如果用户想把所有流量都改成走 3105 代理，最简单的方式是把 Gateway 停止，然后把 3105 改成 3102 的端口。但这可能会影响其他功能。让我问用户具体想怎么改。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你是想把 **所有流量** 都改到 3105 吗？\n\n有几种方式：\n\n| 方式 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **A** | 把 3105 改成 3102 端口（停掉原来的 3102） |\n| **B** | 配置客户端连接 3105（需要知道你的客户端配置在哪） |\n| **C** | 用 nginx/iptables 把 3102 流量转发到 3105 |\n\n你想用哪种方式？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":162360,"output":171,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":162531,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775761437282,"responseId":"chatcmpl-98698ae5-7bb5-4f60-b18b-c99c634115e1"}}
