{"type":"message","id":"185b1bde","parentId":"925b105a","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:17:05.068Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll execute the swap:\n1. First, let's make sure 3105 is properly tested\n2. Then we can swap - but actually we need a safer approach:First make the proxy run on 3102, then stop 3102, then start the proxy on 3102.Wait, the issue is we can't have two services on the same port. The safest way:\n1. Change proxy config to use 3102\n2. Stop 3102\n3. Start proxy on 3102Let me do this step by step.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_555dceb945a440d58aaae973","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 方案：先改代理配置监听 3102（不停原来的 3102，测试是否会报错）\nsed -i 's/PROXY_PORT=3105/PROXY_PORT=3102/' ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env\n\necho \"=== 代理配置 ===\"\ngrep PROXY_PORT ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 测试：启动代理在 3102（预期会失败因为端口被占）===\"\ncd ~/.openclaw/proxy && timeout 3 ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node index.js 2>&1 || true"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":166998,"output":263,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":167261,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775762219294,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ce657be5-9107-4432-81a2-3ecedde2f344"}}
