{"type":"message","id":"dc6303cb","parentId":"4c4af126","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:27:33.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问为什么。让我解释一下发生了什么。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 原因\n\n3102 被多个进程抢占：\n1. **代理进程** (v8 分类评分) - 我启动的\n2. **原 Gateway 进程** - 之前启动的\n\n两个进程都尝试绑定 3102 端口，导致：\n- 谁先启动谁就占用\n- 后启动的会因为端口被占而失败 (EADDRINUSE)\n\n刚才的测试结果混乱就是因为两个进程交替占用，有时走代理，有时走原 Gateway。\n\n现在已停止，你可以重新测试或做其他操作。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":173126,"output":120,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":173246,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775762849964,"responseId":"chatcmpl-845bad08-f168-40e2-bab8-f83949c340b9"}}
