{"type":"message","id":"ae21e87f","parentId":"f6901b8e","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:29:03.029Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to think more about the solution. Let me think about the root cause and better solutions.\n\nRoot cause:\n- Two different services (original Gateway and proxy) both trying to use port 3102\n- No managed way to switch between them\n\nBetter solutions:\n\n1. **Use PM2 process manager** - This is the standard way to manage Node.js services\n   - PM2 can ensure only one process runs on a port\n   - Has built-in restart, logs, and monitoring\n   - Can define ecosystem.config.js to manage both services\n\n2. **Use the script I already created** - but need to make it more robust\n   - Check if port is in use before starting\n   - Use fuser or lsof to find and kill existing process\n\n3. **Actually, the simplest solution**: \n   - Just accept that 3105 is available and works\n   - Client connects to either 3102 (original) or 3105 (with v8)\n   - Both are working, just need client config change\n\n4. **Long-term**: Integrate v8 directly into the Gateway code (not using proxy)\n\nThe user is thinking, so I should wait for their response or provide more thoughtful analysis.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n让我再想想...\n\n## 更深层次的问题\n\n**根本原因**：代理代码和 Gateway 代码是**两套独立的系统**，都在抢同一个端口。\n\n## 更好的长期方案\n\n| 方案 | 长期价值 | 工作量 |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| **A. 集成进 Gateway** | 不需要代理层，架构最简 | 高（需改源码） |\n| **B. 用 PM2 常驻** | 稳定可管理切换 | 低 |\n| **C. 保持现状** | 代理 3105 + Gateway 3102 并存 | 无 |\n\n---\n\n## 其实最简单的方案\n\n**3102 用原 Gateway，3105 用代理**，客户端想用哪个连哪个。\n\n不需要切换，不会冲突。\n\n---\n\n你想用哪个思路？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2568,"output":414,"cacheRead":170752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":173734,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775762918987,"responseId":"019d73b707a4b5debdcc87a68f019187"}}
