{"type":"message","id":"ca532ae3","parentId":"61724933","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:29:28.065Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking for pros and cons of each approach. Let me summarize:\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 各方案优缺点\n\n| 方案 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **A. 集成进 Gateway** | 架构最简，无切换问题 | 工作量大，需改源码，未来升级麻烦 |\n| **B. PM2 常驻** | 稳定可靠，一键切换，有守护 | 仍需手动切换，有竞态风险 |\n| **C. 并存 (3102+3105)** | 最简单，不冲突，各自独立 | 客户端要改配置（但可以二选一测试） |\n\n---\n\n## 我的建议\n\n**方案 C 现状其实最靠谱**：\n- 3102 → 原 Gateway（稳定）\n- 3105 → 代理（测试好的）\n\n客户端想用 v8 分类就配 3105，想用简单版就配 3102。\n\n不用纠结切换，**两个都能用**。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1126,"output":200,"cacheRead":172416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":173742,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775762954457,"responseId":"019d73b84f1f1e7f20def1e296178b50"}}
