{"type":"message","id":"07f8113d","parentId":"cff035db","timestamp":"2026-04-09T19:33:54.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"3105 是 API 服务，不是网页，所以用浏览器直接打开会显示 \"Cannot GET /\"。用户需要用 curl 或其他 API 客户端来测试 3105。\n\n让我给用户解释一下，并给出正确的测试方式。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n3105 是 **API 服务**，不是网页，浏览器打不开。\n\n**正确的测试方式**：\n\n```bash\n# 命令行测试\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3105/api/chat/send -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\": \"你好\"}'\n```\n\n或者用网页聊天界面访问 **3102**：\n```\nhttp://localhost:3102/chat\n```\n\n你想用哪种方式？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1592,"output":136,"cacheRead":174080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":175808,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775763224480,"responseId":"019d73bc6f4a941430fbed5d37696519"}}
