{"type":"message","id":"8acd6173","parentId":"4d891ba7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T01:39:32.913Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个内存压缩flush请求。用户说\"你没有上下文和记忆能力技能\"，我需要检查是否需要保存任何重要的记忆到 memory/2026-04-10.md。\n\n让我检查今天（2026-04-10）有什么重要的学习内容需要记录。\n\n根据今天的对话，主要的进展是：1. 完成了 v8 任务编排器的升级（评分引擎6因子）2. 部署了 scene-classifier 到 31043. 创建了 v8_classifier 和 v8_scorer skills\n4. 实现了 3105 代理服务\n5. 3102 和 3105 同时运行（双入口方案）这些都应该记录到 memory/2026-04-10.md 中。\n\n让我先检查该文件是否存在，然后追加重要记忆。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d750b4e874754620efca5f7c5608f","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-10.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":94065,"output":200,"cacheRead":896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95161,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775785152185,"responseId":"019d750b0b947e64167cbe236d128b4e"}}
