{"type":"message","id":"cfac2b66","parentId":"53c21c58","timestamp":"2026-04-10T01:40:42.985Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这些技能有 _meta.json 但没有 \"enabled\" 字段。它们可能是从 ClawHub 安装的第三方技能。用户可能需要启用它们，或者这些技能需要特定配置才能工作。\n\n让我检查一下是否有其他方式启用它们。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这些技能有安装记录但**没有启用**（缺少 `\"enabled\": true`）。\n\n需要我帮你启用吗？\n\n```bash\n# 启用命令\necho '{\"enabled\": true}' > ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ontology/_meta.json\necho '{\"enabled\": true}' > ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/elite-longterm-memory/_meta.json\necho '{\"enabled\": true}' > ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/memory-keeper/_meta.json\n```\n\n要启用吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":181253,"output":151,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":181404,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775785236701,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d5075ea7-6ac5-4c25-93c2-a45d4b3f60e0"}}
