{"type":"message","id":"d12cfff0","parentId":"7ad67e0b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T01:41:19.737Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问这些记忆技能有没有冲突，以及它们的用处。让我读取这些技能的 SKILL.md 来说明它们的功能。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d750c3b329b59c02a7f25cd613d18","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 读取各技能说明\necho \"=== ontology ===\"\nhead -30 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ontology/SKILL.md\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== elite-longterm-memory ===\"\nhead -30 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/elite-longterm-memory/SKILL.md\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== memory-keeper ===\"\nhead -30 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/memory-keeper/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5018,"output":136,"cacheRead":176128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":181282,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775785264738,"responseId":"019d750c1e56a43c58cd23dddbc823fd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"37ae045d","parentId":"d12cfff0","timestamp":"2026-04-10T01:41:19.843Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d750c3b329b59c02a7f25cd613d18","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ontology ===\n---\nname: ontology\ndescription: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\n---\n\n# Ontology\n\nA typed vocabulary + constraint system for representing knowledge as a verifiable graph.\n\n## Core Concept\n\nEverything is an **entity** with a **type**, **properties**, and **relations** to other entities. Every mutation is validated against type constraints before committing.\n\n```\nEntity: { id, type, properties, relations, created, updated }\nRelation: { from_id, relation_type, to_id, properties }\n```\n\n## When to Use\n\n| Trigger | Action |\n|---------|--------|\n| \"Remember that...\" | Create/update entity |\n| \"What do I know about X?\" | Query graph |\n| \"Link X to Y\" | Create relation |\n| \"Show all tasks for project Z\" | Graph traversal |\n| \"What depends on X?\" | Dependency query |\n| Planning multi-step work | Model as graph transformations |\n| Skill needs shared state | Read/write ontology objects |\n\n\n=== elite-longterm-memory ===\n---\nname: elite-longterm-memory\nversion: 1.2.3\ndescription: \"Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\"\nauthor: NextFrontierBuilds\nkeywords: [memory, ai-agent, ai-coding, long-term-memory, vector-search, lancedb, git-notes, wal, persistent-context, claude, claude-code, gpt, chatgpt, cursor, copilot, github-copilot, openclaw, moltbot, vibe-coding, agentic, ai-tools, developer-tools, devtools, typescript, llm, automation]\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    emoji: \"🧠\"\n    requires:\n      env:\n        - OPENAI_API_KEY\n      plugins:\n        - memory-lancedb\n---\n\n# Elite Longterm Memory 🧠\n\n**The ultimate memory system for AI agents.** Combines 6 proven approaches into one bulletproof architecture.\n\nNever lose context. Never forget decisions. Never repeat mistakes.\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    ELITE LONGTERM MEMORY                        │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐             │\n\n=== memory-keeper ===\n# Memory Keeper Agent\n\n> 自动化记忆维护 Agent\n\n## 用途\n\n定期整理和优化长期记忆系统。\n\n## 核心职责\n\n1. **扫描** - 读取 `memory/` 下所有文件\n2. **去重** - 合并重复信息\n3. **清理** - 删除过期条目（根据 `[expires: YYYY-MM-DD]` 标记）\n4. **提取** - 将 `ephemeral/` 中有价值的信息迁移到主记忆\n5. **更新** - 刷新 `MEMORY.md` 的 `last_updated` 时间戳\n\n## 触发方式\n\n```bash\n# 手动运行\n~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_keeper.sh\n\n# 或通过 cron 每日运行\n# 建议时间: 每天 04:00 (维护脚本之后)\n```\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n每日日志 (memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":63,"aggregated":"=== ontology ===\n---\nname: ontology\ndescription: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\n---\n\n# Ontology\n\nA typed vocabulary + constraint system for representing knowledge as a verifiable graph.\n\n## Core Concept\n\nEverything is an **entity** with a **type**, **properties**, and **relations** to other entities. Every mutation is validated against type constraints before committing.\n\n```\nEntity: { id, type, properties, relations, created, updated }\nRelation: { from_id, relation_type, to_id, properties }\n```\n\n## When to Use\n\n| Trigger | Action |\n|---------|--------|\n| \"Remember that...\" | Create/update entity |\n| \"What do I know about X?\" | Query graph |\n| \"Link X to Y\" | Create relation |\n| \"Show all tasks for project Z\" | Graph traversal |\n| \"What depends on X?\" | Dependency query |\n| Planning multi-step work | Model as graph transformations |\n| Skill needs shared state | Read/write ontology objects |\n\n\n=== elite-longterm-memory ===\n---\nname: elite-longterm-memory\nversion: 1.2.3\ndescription: \"Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\"\nauthor: NextFrontierBuilds\nkeywords: [memory, ai-agent, ai-coding, long-term-memory, vector-search, lancedb, git-notes, wal, persistent-context, claude, claude-code, gpt, chatgpt, cursor, copilot, github-copilot, openclaw, moltbot, vibe-coding, agentic, ai-tools, developer-tools, devtools, typescript, llm, automation]\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    emoji: \"🧠\"\n    requires:\n      env:\n        - OPENAI_API_KEY\n      plugins:\n        - memory-lancedb\n---\n\n# Elite Longterm Memory 🧠\n\n**The ultimate memory system for AI agents.** Combines 6 proven approaches into one bulletproof architecture.\n\nNever lose context. Never forget decisions. Never repeat mistakes.\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    ELITE LONGTERM MEMORY                        │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐             │\n\n=== memory-keeper ===\n# Memory Keeper Agent\n\n> 自动化记忆维护 Agent\n\n## 用途\n\n定期整理和优化长期记忆系统。\n\n## 核心职责\n\n1. **扫描** - 读取 `memory/` 下所有文件\n2. **去重** - 合并重复信息\n3. **清理** - 删除过期条目（根据 `[expires: YYYY-MM-DD]` 标记）\n4. **提取** - 将 `ephemeral/` 中有价值的信息迁移到主记忆\n5. **更新** - 刷新 `MEMORY.md` 的 `last_updated` 时间戳\n\n## 触发方式\n\n```bash\n# 手动运行\n~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_keeper.sh\n\n# 或通过 cron 每日运行\n# 建议时间: 每天 04:00 (维护脚本之后)\n```\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n每日日志 (memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775785279832}}
{"type":"message","id":"24f4e683","parentId":"37ae045d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T01:41:42.251Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我可以解释这三个技能的区别和是否有冲突了。让我总结一下。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 各技能用途\n\n| 技能 | 功能 | 触发词 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| **ontology** | 知识图谱，结构化记忆（实体+关系） | \"记住\"、\"查询\"、\"链接\" |\n| **elite-longterm-memory** | 长期记忆系统（WAL协议 + 向量搜索） | 自动后台运行 |\n| **memory-keeper** | 记忆维护（去重、清理、迁移） | 定时任务 |\n\n---\n\n## 是否有冲突？\n\n**有一定功能重叠**，但不完全冲突：\n- ontology → 知识图谱（结构化）\n- elite-longterm-memory → **完整记忆系统**（向量+持久化）\n- memory-keeper → 维护脚本（辅助）\n\n**建议**：如果启用 elite-longterm-memory，它已经很强大了，ontology 可以作为补充。\n\n要我帮你启用吗？或者先测试一下它们的具体效果？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":925,"output":199,"cacheRead":181120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":182244,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775785279854,"responseId":"019d750cfc680ffea24c842231c9e6a5"}}
