{"type":"compaction","id":"a9025604","parentId":"87d0fc37","timestamp":"2026-04-10T02:10:28.051Z","summary":"\n\n## Goal\nIntegrate v8 scoring and classification services into OpenClaw so that WebChat messages are classified and scored before processing. The flow is: WebChat → classification (3104) → scene handling → scoring (3103) → strategy routing.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Keep v8 task orchestrator on port 3103 (already running)\n- Use scene-classifier on port 3104 (moved from 8080)\n- Create proxy service to avoid modifying Gateway source code directly\n- Implement circuit breaker and fallback logic for resilience\n- Gateway accepts /api/chat/send on port 3102\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Modified scene-classifier port from 8080 to 3104\n- [x] Created systemd service for scene-classifier auto-start\n- [x] Added circuit breaker/fallback logic to scene-classifier (api_server.py)\n- [x] Created v8_classifier skill at ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/\n- [x] Created v8_scorer skill at ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_scorer/\n- [x] Updated AGENTS.md with new preprocessing flow\n- [x] Created v8Client.ts at /home/ai/openclaw-listener/src/clients/v8Client.ts\n- [x] Modified MessageHandler to use v8 classification/score instead of old Gateway APIs\n- [x] Fixed listener config: changed gateway WebSocket url from ws://127.0.0.1:3103 to ws://127.0.0.1:3102\n- [x] Created proxy service at ~/.openclaw/proxy/ on port 3105\n- [x] Fixed proxy routing issues - removed _proxy metadata from forwarded requests\n- [x] Verified curl tests: 3105 correctly routes chitchat and scored messages to 3102\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Configure WebChat client to connect to port 3105 instead of 3102\n\n### Blocked\n- Control UI (port 3110) returns \"Unauthorized\" - authentication issue not fully resolved. Workaround: set localStorage.setItem('authToken', '0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced') in browser console\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Port 3104 for classifier**: 3103 was already occupied by v8 task orchestrator\n- **Proxy approach**: Created forward proxy on 3105 rather than modifying Gateway source code (compiled dist)\n- **Gateway port 3102**: Not 3108 - the actual Gateway accepts /api/chat/send on 3102\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Locate WebChat client configuration and change API endpoint from 3102 to 3105\n2. Or provide user instructions to modify their WebChat client\n3. Alternatively, use socat/iptables to redirect traffic from 3102 to 3105\n\n## Critical Context\n- v8 scoring service: http://localhost:3103/api/score\n- scene-classifier: http://localhost:3104/classify\n- proxy (v8-enabled Gateway): http://localhost:3105/api/chat/send\n- original Gateway: http://localhost:3102/api/chat/send\n- Control UI: http://localhost:3110/?token=0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced (auth issue workaround available)\n- listener: http://localhost:3106/health (connected: true)\n- 测试任务ID：1d69cb64-172d-4d91-a99f-3f34af614ca3\n- Node 版本：v22.22.1\n\n## Decisions\n- 采用 v8 评分引擎的 6 因子 + 平方根归一化 + 组合规则，删除对 v7 adapter 的依赖\n- 从 workspace 复制 scene-classifier 到 v8/scene-classifier/，不从头创建\n- 技能任务（type=skill）绕过 command 验证，直接调用 skillLoader 执行\n- auto_improve 技能使用 (goal, projectPath, maxIterations) 参数格式调用\n- 采用 proxy 方案避免修改 Gateway 源码（编译后的 dist）\n- 分类器端口从 8080 改为 3104（3103 已被 v8 task orchestrator 占用）\n- Gateway 端口使用 3102（非 3108）\n\n## Open TODOs\n- 统一分类器端口：当前 8080，建议改为 3103 与设计一致（已改为 3104）\n- 验证分类器熔断降级：停止分类器 Python 服务，测试 v8 自动降级\n- 配置开机自启（可选）：为分类器创建 systemd 服务（已完成）\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- v8 评分因子：logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, dependency (各 0-3 分)\n- 归一化公式：sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100\n- 组合规则：duration>=3 && dependency>=2 → MEGA_TASK; risk>=3 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT; resource>=3 → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n\n## Pending user asks\n- 用户给出 3 个微调建议，等待用户确认是否执行\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- v8 服务端口：3103\n- scene-classifier 端口：3104（原 8080）\n- proxy 端口：3105\n- 原始 Gateway 端口：3102\n- Control UI 端口：3110\n- listener 端口：3106\n- 任务编排目录：~/.openclaw/v8/src/\n- 技能目录：~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/auto_improve/\n- 测试任务ID：1d69cb64-172d-4d91-a99f-3f34af614ca3\n- Node 版本：v22.22.1\n- 用户角色：openclaw-control-ui\n- authToken: 0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced\n- 时间戳：Fri 2026-04-10 01:34 GMT+8\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n\n## Decisions\n- 用户正在排查 \"openclaw-control-ui\" 应用通过网页打开时的配置位置\n\n## Open TODOs\n- 找出 \"openclaw-control-ui\" 应用的 Web 服务器配置或静态文件路径\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- (none)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- 用户想知道他们的网页应用配置在哪里（通过网页打开但找不到配置）\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- label: \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n- id: \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n- 时间: Fri 2026-04-10 03:08 GMT+8\n- 端口: 80 (LISTEN 状态)\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 03:02 GMT+8] 修改配置干嘛\n- Assistant: 之前说可以把 WebChat 从连接 **3102** 改成连接 **3105**，就能用上分类和评分了。\n\n但如果你不需要这个，**就不用改**。\n\n你现在用的 3102 也能正常聊天，只是没有分类评分功能。\n\n**不折腾了，继续用 3102 吧。**\n\n有其他需要吗？\n[non-text content: thinking]\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 03:03 GMT+8] 需要的\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): ---\n/home/ai/.openclaw/.env:ROUTER_PORT=3102\n/home/ai/.openclaw/proxy/.env:GATEWAY_URL=http://localhost:3102\n/home/ai/.openclaw/proxy/index.js:const GATEWAY_URL = process.env.GATEWAY_URL || 'http://localhost:3102';\n/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/7a24d998-baf8-4cd6-8eef-04327e46591e.jsonl.reset.2026-04-09T11-22-35.864Z:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"5b2dd038\",\"parentId\":\"364bdbdb\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-08T17:05:01.485Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"019d6e0d27c4ddf8f5d546b63f3bb116\",\"toolName\":\"read\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"const express = require('express');\\nconst { ...\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking