ateway\npm2 stop gateway # 或 pkill -f \"gateway.*3102\"\n# 修改代理配置，将 PROXY_PORT 改为 3102，重启代理\n- Assistant: 方案很好 👍\n\n但我需要知道你的 **WebChat 客户端配置在哪里** 才能改。\n\n你用的是哪种方式连接 Gateway？\n1. 浏览器访问某个网址（什么网址？）\n2. 桌面客户端软件（什么软件？）\n3. 命令行 curl\n\n告诉我具体情况，我帮你改配置。\n[non-text content: thinking]\n\n## Tool Failures\n- write: Validation failed for tool \"write\": - content: must be string Received arguments: { \"content\": { \"name\": \"v8_scorer\", \"version\": \"1.0.0\", \"description\": \"调用 v8 评分引擎，评估任务复杂度并返回执行策略\", \"main\": \"index.js\", \"dependencies\": { \"axios\": \"^1.6.0\"...\n- write: Validation failed for tool \"write\": - content: must be string Received arguments: { \"content\": { \"name\": \"v8_scorer\", \"version\": \"1.0.0\", \"description\": \"调用 v8 评分引擎，评估任务复杂度并返回执行策略\", \"main\": \"index.js\", \"dependencies\": { \"axios\": \"^1.6.0\"...\n\n<read-files>\n/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/on-message.sh\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/context/ContextProtector.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/executor/ExecutionGuard.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/index.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/persistence/TaskStore.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scheduler/Scheduler.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/adapter.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/engine.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/security/RateLimiter.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/security/SecurityGateway.js\n/home/ai/openclaw-listener/src/apiClient.ts\n\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/home/ai/.openclaw/proxy/clients/v8Client.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/proxy/index.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/api_server.py\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/scene-classifier.service\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/executor/SandboxExecutor.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/router/api.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/skills/skillLoader.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/index.js\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/package.json\n/home/ai/.op