{"type":"message","id":"45048ee2","parentId":"9682e151","timestamp":"2026-04-10T02:31:19.219Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 10:31 GMT+8] 先评分，学习，给出预案并思考：# OpenClaw v8 智能入口\n\n---\n\n## 一、最终架构\n\n```\n客户端 (WebChat / API)\n │\n ▼\n Proxy :3102 (原 Gateway 端口)\n ├─ HTTP /api/chat/send → 分类(3104) → 评分(3103) → 提交 v8 任务\n ├─ WebSocket /ws → 转发至 Gateway (3101) 处理实时推送\n ├─ 上下文管理 → 调用 Context API (3101)\n └─ 健康检查 /health\n │\n ▼\n Gateway :3101 (原 Gateway 降级为 WebSocket 后端，仅处理长连接)\n v8 服务 :3103 (评分+任务)\n 分类器 :3104\n 上下文 API :3101 (独立服务，可复用 Gateway 端口)\n```\n\n**关键设计**：\n- **端口统一**：代理占据 `3102`，客户端无感知。\n- **WebSocket 分离**：代理将 `/ws` 升级请求转发给原 Gateway (`3101`)。\n- **上下文独立**：Context API 单独部署在 `3101`（与 Gateway 同端口但不同路径），代理在需要时调用。\n\n---\n\n## 二、部署前准备\n\n### 2.1 确认现有服务\n```bash\nss -tlnp | grep -E \"3101|3102|3103|3104\"\n```\n预期：\n- 3102: 原 Gateway（将被替换）\n- 3103: v8 评分/任务\n- 3104: 分类器\n\n### 2.2 调整原 Gateway 至 3101\n```bash\nopenclaw config set gateway.port 3101\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n验证：\n```bash\ncurl http://localhost:3101/health\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、代理服务完整代码（含 WebSocket 与上下文调用）\n\n### 3.1 目录结构\n```\n~/.openclaw/proxy/\n├── index.js\n├── package.json\n├── .env\n├── ecosystem.config.js\n├── clients/\n│ └── v8Client.js # 同前，分类/评分客户端\n└── logs/\n```\n\n### 3.2 `package.json`\n```json\n{\n \"name\": \"openclaw-proxy\",\n \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n \"main\": \"index.js\",\n \"dependencies\": {\n \"express\": \"^4.18.2\",\n \"axios\": \"^1.6.0\",\n \"ws\": \"^8.14.2\",\n \"dotenv\": \"^16.0.3\",\n \"pino\": \"^8.17.2\"\n }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.3 `.env`\n```bash\nPROXY_PORT=3102\nCLASSIFIER_URL=http://localhost:3104/classify\nSCORER_URL=http://localhost:3103/api/score\nV8_TASK_API=http://localhost:3103/api/task\nGATEWAY_WS_URL=ws://localhost:3101/ws\nCONTEXT_API_URL=http://localhost:3101/api/context\nADMIN_TOKEN=<随机生成>\nBYPASS_MODE=false\n```\n\n### 3.4 `index.js`（核心逻辑）\n\n```javascript\nrequire('dotenv').config();\nconst express = require('express');\nconst http = require('http');\nconst axios = require('axios');\nconst WebSocket = require('ws');\nconst pino = require('pino');\nconst { classify, score } = require('./clients/v8Client');\n\nconst app = express();\napp.use(express.json());\n\nconst PORT = process.env.PROXY_PORT || 3102;\nconst BYPASS_MODE = process.env.BYPASS_MODE === 'true';\nconst V8_TASK_API = process.env.V8_TASK_API;\nconst GATEWAY_WS_URL = process.env.GATEWAY_WS_URL;\nconst CONTEXT_API_URL = process.env.CONTEXT_API_URL;\nconst ADMIN_TOKEN = process.env.ADMIN_TOKEN || 'change-me';\n\nconst logger = pino({ level: process.env.LOG_LEVEL || 'info' });\n\n// ==================== 辅助函数 ====================\nasync function getContext() {\n try {\n const res = await axios.get(`${CONTEXT_API_URL}/full`, { timeout: 2000 });\n return res.data.messages || [];\n } catch { return []; }\n}\n\nasync function saveContext(role, content) {\n try {\n await axios.post(CONTEXT_API_URL, { role, content }, { timeout: 2000 });\n } catch { /* 降级忽略 */ }\n}\n\nfunction getNonTaskReply(scene) {\n const replies = { chitchat: '你好！有什么技术问题？', fault_recovery: '请描述故障现象...' };\n return replies[scene] || '收到消息。';\n}\n\nasync function submitV8Task(message, scoring) {\n const payload = {\n type: 'command',\n command: message.trim().split(/\\s+/)[0] || 'echo',\n args: message.trim().split(/\\s+/).slice(1),\n timeout: scoring.timeout,\n priority: Math.floor(scoring.score / 20),\n metadata: { prompt: message, strategy: scoring.recommendedStrategy }\n };\n const res = await axios.post(V8_TASK_API, payload, { timeout: 5000 });\n return res.data.id;\n}\n\n// ==================== HTTP 处理 ====================\napp.post('/api/chat/send', async (req, res) => {\n const { message, sessionId } = req.body;\n if (!message) return res.status(400).json({ error: 'message required' });\n\n if (BYPASS_MODE) {\n return res.json({ reply: `[Bypass] 收到：${message}` });\n }\n\n try {\n // 1. 获取历史上下文\n const history = await getContext();\n // 2. 分类\n const cls = await classify(message);\n logger.info({ scene: cls.scene, isTask: cls.isTask }, 'Classified');\n // 3. 保存用户消息\n await saveContext('user', message);\n\n if (!cls.isTask) {\n const reply = getNonTaskReply(cls.scene);\n await saveContext('assistant', reply);\n return res.json({ reply, scene: cls.scene });\n }\n\n // 4. 评分\n const scr = await score(message, { history });\n logger.info({ score: scr.score, strategy: scr.recommendedStrategy }, 'Scored');\n // 5. 提交任务\n const taskId = await submitV8Task(message, scr);\n const reply = `✅ 任务已提交 (ID: ${taskId})，预计 ${scr.timeout}s。`;\n await saveContext('assistant', reply);\n res.json({ reply, taskId, strategy: scr.recommendedStrategy });\n } catch (err) {\n logger.error(err, 'HTTP processing error');\n res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal error' });\n }\n});\n\napp.get('/health', (req, res) => res.json({ status: 'ok', bypass: BYPASS_MODE }));\napp.post('/admin/bypass', (req, res) => {\n if (req.headers['x-admin-token'] !== ADMIN_TOKEN) return res.status(401).end();\n BYPASS_MODE = req.body.enabled === true;\n res.json({ bypass: BYPASS_MODE });\n});\n\n// ==================== WebSocket 代理 ====================\nconst server = http.createServer(app);\nconst wss = new WebSocket.Server({ noServer: true });\n\nwss.on('connection', (clientWs, req) => {\n logger.info('WebSocket client connected');\n const targetWs = new WebSocket(GATEWAY_WS_URL);\n clientWs.on('message', (msg) => targetWs.send(msg));\n targetWs.on('message', (msg) => clientWs.send(msg));\n clientWs.on('close', () => targetWs.close());\n targetWs.on('close', () => clientWs.close());\n clientWs.on('error', (e) => logger.error(e, 'Client WS error'));\n targetWs.on('error', (e) => logger.error(e, 'Target WS error'));\n});\n\nserver.on('upgrade', (req, socket, head) => {\n // 只处理 /ws 或根路径的升级请求（根据 Gateway 实际情况调整）\n if (req.url === '/ws' || req.url === '/') {\n wss.handleUpgrade(req, socket, head, (ws) => {\n wss.emit('connection', ws, req);\n });\n } else {\n socket.destroy();\n }\n});\n\nserver.listen(PORT, () => logger.info(`Proxy listening on ${PORT}`));\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、部署步骤\n\n### 4.1 安装依赖并启动代理\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/proxy\nnpm install\npm2 start ecosystem.config.js\npm2 save\n```\n\n### 4.2 切换端口（停止原 3102，启动代理）\n使用之前提供的强化切换脚本 `openclaw-gateway-switch`：\n```bash\nopenclaw-gateway-switch proxy\n```\n\n### 4.3 验证\n```bash\n# HTTP\ncurl http://localhost:3102/health\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/chat/send -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\":\"你好\"}'\n# WebSocket（通过浏览器访问 http://localhost:3102/chat 并查看网络面板）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、回退预案\n\n```bash\nopenclaw-gateway-switch gateway\n```\n30秒内恢复原 Gateway 在 3102 服务。\n\n---\n\n## 六、监控建议\n\n- 代理日志：`pm2 logs openclaw-proxy`\n- 上下文状态：`curl http://localhost:3101/api/context/status`\n- 依赖健康：`curl http://localhost:3102/health`\n\n---\n\n## 七、多轮修正总结\n\n| 迭代 | 问题 | 解决方案 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 1 | 代理仅 HTTP，WebChat WebSocket 断开 | 增加 `ws` 库，实现 WebSocket 升级转发 |\n| 2 | 上下文未持久化，LLM 缺乏历史 | 集成独立的 Context API (3101) |\n| 3 | 硬编码配置不便维护 | 全部环境变量化，提供 `.env` 示例 |\n| 4 | 故障恢复依赖手动 | 强化切换脚本，加入健康检查和自动回滚 |\n| 5 | 缺少结构化日志 | 引入 `pino`，关键路径可追踪 |"}],"timestamp":1775788279209}}
