{"type":"message","id":"8a6b6b28","parentId":"08ef2af9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T02:39:57.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题找到了！系统启动时可能有多个自动脚本：1. 3101 还是旧的 context-api（启动顺序问题）2. 3102 是代理\n\n让我检查更详细的情况，修正启动顺序。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d754260449efa421495896edff383","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 停止所有进程并按正确顺序启动\necho \"1. 停止所有\"\nfuser -k 3101/tcp 3102/tcp 3106/tcp 2>/dev/null || true\nsleep 2\n\necho \"2. 启动 Context API (3106)\"\ncd ~/.openclaw/context-api && nohup ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node index.js > logs/ctx.log 2>&1 &\nsleep 2\n\necho \"3. 启动 Gateway (3101)\"\ncd ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw && nohup ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node openclaw.mjs gateway start > /tmp/gw.log 2>&1 &\nsleep 3\n\necho \"4. 启动代理 (3102)\"\ncd ~/.openclaw/proxy && nohup ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node index.js > /tmp/proxy.log 2>&1 &\nsleep 2\n\necho \"=== 最终状态 ===\"\nss -tlnp | grep -E \"3101|3102|3103|3104|3106\"","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1105,"output":329,"cacheRead":59520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60954,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775788769248,"responseId":"019d75422e87bfe83975014280cf92d7"}}
