{"type":"message","id":"6fc3f68f","parentId":"146f7f47","timestamp":"2026-04-10T02:43:31.028Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问现在是什么情况。让我简洁回答。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 当前情况\n\n3101 不是 Gateway，是**旧版的 context-api**（之前备份的）。\n\n**3102 现在走的是原 Gateway**，不是代理。\n\n## 问题\n\n1. Gateway 启动失败 / 启动到了错误的进程\n2. 代理也没在 3102 正常运行\n\n## 需要\n\n先确认 Gateway 怎么启动：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n还是你手动指定的方式？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2244,"output":97,"cacheRead":59520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61861,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775789002549,"responseId":"019d7545ba1483456ba334771a19f7b7"}}
