{"type":"message","id":"15c25621","parentId":"44878119","timestamp":"2026-04-10T02:48:57.250Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 10:48 GMT+8] ai@ai:~$ ps aux | grep -E \"openclaw-gateway|gateway.*3102\"\nai 11352 9.6 3.2 22764296 597252 ? Ssl 10:39 0:44 openclaw-gateway\nai 12336 0.0 0.0 8188 2432 pts/4 S+ 10:47 0:00 grep --color=auto -E openclaw-gateway|gateway.*3102\nai@ai:~$ openclaw gateway status\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.9 (0512059) — I'm not magic—I'm just extremely persistent with retries and coping strategies.\n\n│\n◇\nService: systemd (enabled)\nFile logs: /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-10.log\nCommand: /usr/bin/node /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 3108\nService file: ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service\nService env: OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=3108\n\nConfig (cli): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\nConfig (service): ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n\nGateway: bind=loopback (127.0.0.1), port=3108 (service args)\nProbe target: ws://127.0.0.1:3108\nDashboard: http://127.0.0.1:3108/\nProbe note: Loopback-only gateway; only local clients can connect.\n\nRuntime: running (pid 11352, state active, sub running, last exit 0, reason 0)\nRPC probe: ok\n\nListening: 127.0.0.1:3108\nTroubles: run openclaw status\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting\nai@ai:~$"}],"timestamp":1775789337237}}
{"type":"message","id":"4de2e770","parentId":"15c25621","timestamp":"2026-04-10T02:49:20.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了！Gateway 实际上运行在 **3108** 端口，不是 3101！\n\n- Gateway 服务：port=3108 (通过 systemd 启动)\n- 3102 是另一个进程（之前手动启动的旧版 openclaw-router）\n- 3101 是旧版 context-api (备份)\n\n用户想要的是：\n- 3102 - 新的代理 (v8 分类+评分+上下文)\n- 3101 - 可以释放出来给 Gateway 或者其他服务\n- 3108 - Gateway 当前端口\n\n现在需要重新规划：\n- 让 Gateway 用 3101？或者保持 3108？\n- 代理需要 WebSocket 支持\n\n让我重新理解用户的需求并给出新的方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 明白了！\n\n**Gateway 实际运行在 3108**，不是 3101/3102。\n\n```\nps aux 显示: openclaw-gateway 监听 3108\n```\n\n## 当前正确的端口分配\n\n| 端口 | 服务 |\n|------|------|\n| 3102 | 旧版 openclaw-router (旧 context-api) |\n| 3103 | v8 评分 |\n| 3104 | 分类器 |\n| 3106 | 新版 Context API |\n| 3108 | Gateway (systemd 服务) |\n\n---\n\n## 问题\n\n你的方案要求：\n- 3102 = 代理（含 WebSocket）\n- 3101 = Gateway (WebSocket 后端)\n\n但 Gateway 已经用 systemd 跑在 3108 了。\n\n**两个选择**：\n1. **改 Gateway 到 3101**：`openclaw config set gateway.port 3101 && openclaw gateway restart`\n2. **保持现状**：代理用 3105，Gateway 用 3108\n\n你想用哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":61154,"output":358,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62664,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775789337268,"responseId":"019d754ae6ae5991a510fd16f399db22"}}
