{"type":"message","id":"8583b858","parentId":"c0c28f8f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T02:56:48.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"3102 是 Gateway API 服务！所以代理应该用 3102 而不是 3108。\n\n之前代理配置被改成了 3108，需要改回 3102。同时 WebSocket 也应该是 3102。\n\n让我更新代理配置并重启。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a96b2da101ae4508a96716e5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 修复代理配置，使用 3102 作为 Gateway\nsed -i 's|GATEWAY_URL=.*|GATEWAY_URL=http://localhost:3102|' ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env\nsed -i 's|GATEWAY_WS=.*|GATEWAY_WS=ws://localhost:3102|' ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env\n\n# 重启代理\nfuser -k 3105/tcp 2>/dev/null || true\nsleep 2\ncd ~/.openclaw/proxy && nohup ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node index.js > /tmp/proxy.log 2>&1 &\nsleep 3\n\n# 测试\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3105/api/chat/send \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\": \"帮我重构代码\"}'","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":70160,"output":270,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775789803122,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4154f0d7-1e24-46fa-8dd5-911214ab1a0d"}}
