{"type":"message","id":"174b8844","parentId":"e48b363b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:09:11.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要方案3的详细实施步骤。让我思考一下：\n\n方案3：代理移到 3102 替换原 Gateway\n\n步骤：\n1. 停止原 Gateway (3102)\n2. 修改代理配置监听 3102\n3. 启动代理在 3102\n4. 测试\n\n但问题是 Gateway 原本在 3108 通过 systemd 运行，3102 上运行的是另一个进程（旧版 router）。让我理清楚当前的状态：\n\n- 3102: 旧版 openclaw-router (不是 Gateway)\n- 3105: 代理\n\n所以其实可以直接把代理移到 3102，不需要停掉 Gateway（因为 Gateway 在 3108）。\n\n让我告诉用户具体步骤。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 方案3 实施步骤\n\n**当前状态**：\n- 3102 是旧版 router（可以停掉）\n- 3105 是代理\n- Gateway 在 3108\n\n**步骤**：\n\n1. **停止 3102 上的旧 router**\n   ```bash\n   fuser -k 3102/tcp\n   ```\n\n2. **修改代理配置为 3102**\n   ```bash\n   sed -i 's/PROXY_PORT=3105/PROXY_PORT=3102/' ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env\n   ```\n\n3. **重启代理**\n   ```bash\n   cd ~/.openclaw/proxy && node index.js\n   ```\n\n4. **验证**\n   - 访问 http://localhost:3102/chat.html\n   - 或 http://localhost:3102/ 应该显示聊天界面\n\n---\n\n**结果**：3102 变成智能代理入口，有分类+评分功能。\n\n做吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":70548,"output":340,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72040,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775790529383,"responseId":"019d755d1557711b4ca1acba03e727a5"}}
{"type":"custom","customType":"openclaw:bootstrap-context:full","data":{"timestamp":1775790551068,"runId":"254b1dea-c3b1-4609-b98c-36047fa59964","sessionId":"122589c7-91b3-43f3-93c5-2d5af138e58c"},"id":"a9f66f3b","parentId":"174b8844","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:09:11.068Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"495711ce","parentId":"a9f66f3b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:11:15.674Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 11:11 GMT+8] 看看这个方案，回答我：一、前置检查清单（执行前务必确认）\nbash\n# 1. 确认当前服务状态\nss -tlnp | grep -E \"3101|3102|3103|3104|3105\"\n\n# 2. 确认切换脚本存在且可执行\nls -l /usr/local/bin/openclaw-gateway-switch\n\n# 3. 确认代理目录完整\nls ~/.openclaw/proxy/{index.js,package.json,ecosystem.config.js,.env}\n\n# 4. 确认原 Gateway 可正常启动\nopenclaw gateway status\n二、终极执行脚本（全自动，含自动回滚）\n将以下内容保存为 ~/final-switch.sh，赋予执行权限 chmod +x ~/final-switch.sh，然后执行。\n\nbash\n#!/bin/bash\nset -euo pipefail\n\nLOG_FILE=\"/tmp/openclaw-switch-$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S).log\"\nexec > >(tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\") 2>&1\n\necho \"=== OpenClaw 智能入口切换开始 $(date) ===\"\n\n# ---------- 1. 清理冲突端口 ----------\necho \"[1/6] 清理 3101 端口占用...\"\nfuser -k 3101/tcp 2>/dev/null || true\nsleep 1\n\n# ---------- 2. 迁移原 Gateway 至 3101 ----------\necho \"[2/6] 迁移 Gateway 至 3101...\"\nopenclaw config set gateway.port 3101\nopenclaw gateway restart\nsleep 3\n\n# 验证 Gateway 在 3101 是否就绪\nif curl -s --max-time 5 http://localhost:3101/health >/dev/null; then\n echo \"✅ Gateway 已在 3101 正常运行\"\nelse\n echo \"❌ Gateway 在 3101 启动失败，回退...\"\n openclaw config set gateway.port 3102\n openclaw gateway restart\n exit 1\nfi\n\n# ---------- 3. 确保代理支持 WebSocket ----------\necho \"[3/6] 检查代理 WebSocket 支持...\"\ncd ~/.openclaw/proxy\nif ! grep -q \"server.on('upgrade'\" index.js; then\n echo \"⚠️ 代理代码缺少 WebSocket 支持，请先更新 index.js！\"\n exit 1\nfi\n\n# ---------- 4. 启动代理（若未运行）----------\necho \"[4/6] 启动代理服务...\"\npm2 restart openclaw-proxy 2>/dev/null || pm2 start ecosystem.config.js\npm2 save\nsleep 2\n\n# ---------- 5. 执行端口切换 ----------\necho \"[5/6] 执行代理接管 3102...\"\nif ! openclaw-gateway-switch proxy; then\n echo \"❌ 切换失败，正在回退...\"\n openclaw-gateway-switch gateway\n exit 1\nfi\n\n# ---------- 6. 最终验证 ----------\necho \"[6/6] 最终验证...\"\nsleep 2\n\n# HTTP 验证\nif curl -s --max-time 5 http://localhost:3102/health | grep -q \"ok\"; then\n echo \"✅ HTTP 服务正常\"\nelse\n echo \"❌ HTTP 服务异常\"\n openclaw-gateway-switch gateway\n exit 1\nfi\n\n# WebSocket 验证（模拟升级请求）\nif curl -s -H \"Upgrade: websocket\" -H \"Connection: Upgrade\" --max-time 3 \\\n http://localhost:3102/ws 2>&1 | grep -q \"101\"; then\n echo \"✅ WebSocket 升级正常\"\nelse\n echo \"⚠️ WebSocket 升级验证未明确返回 101，但可能仍可用\"\nfi\n\n# 依赖服务检查\ncurl -s http://localhost:3103/health >/dev/null && echo \"✅ v8 评分器正常\" || echo \"⚠️ v8 评分器无响应\"\ncurl -s http://localhost:3104/health >/dev/null && echo \"✅ 分类器正常\" || echo \"⚠️ 分类器无响应\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 切换成功 ===\"\necho \"日志保存在: $LOG_FILE\"\necho \"访问 http://localhost:3102/chat 体验智能增强版 WebChat\"\necho \"如有问题，执行回退: openclaw-gateway-switch gateway\"\n三、执行与观察\nbash\nchmod +x ~/final-switch.sh\n./final-switch.sh\n执行过程中，脚本会：\n\n自动清理 3101 端口\n\n迁移 Gateway 并验证健康\n\n检查代理 WebSocket 支持\n\n执行切换并验证 HTTP/WebSocket\n\n任何步骤失败均自动回退\n\n四、代理 index.js 必备代码片段（确保 WebSocket 正确转发）\n若你尚未更新代理，请用以下关键代码替换/补全：\n\njavascript\n// ... 其他 express 初始化 ...\nconst server = http.createServer(app);\nconst wss = new WebSocket.Server({ noServer: true });\n\nwss.on('connection', (ws, req) => {\n const target = new WebSocket(process.env.GATEWAY_WS_URL || 'ws://localhost:3101/ws');\n ws.on('message', msg => target.send(msg));\n target.on('message', msg => ws.send(msg));\n ws.on('close', () => target.close());\n target.on('close', () => ws.close());\n});\n\nserver.on('upgrade', (req, socket, head) => {\n if (req.url === '/ws' || req.url === '/') {\n wss.handleUpgrade(req, socket, head, ws => wss.emit('connection', ws, req));\n } else {\n socket.destroy();\n }\n});\n\nserver.listen(PORT, ...);\n五、回退预案\n若切换后 WebChat 出现异常（如页面空白、消息无响应），立即执行：\n\nbash\nopenclaw-gateway-switch gateway\n30 秒内恢复原状，Gateway 回到 3102 端口。"}],"timestamp":1775790675663}}
{"type":"message","id":"07febbdf","parentId":"495711ce","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:11:20.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户给了一个完整的方案。让我分析一下：方案有几个问题：\n\n1. 方案要求把 Gateway 迁移到 3101，但 3101 当前有旧版 router（旧的 context-api）\n2. 方案需要创建切换脚本，需要 openclaw-gateway-switch 命令存在\n3. 方案假设 Gateway 可以通过 openclaw config set gateway.port 3101 来修改端口但实际上 Gateway 是通过 systemd 服务运行的，配置文件可能不是直接用 openclaw config\n\n让我检查一下当前状态，然后给用户分析。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a788e58701a74a4694e514f7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查当前端口 ===\"\nss -tlnp | grep -E \"3101|3102|3103|3104|3105\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 检查切换脚本 ===\"\nls -la /usr/local/bin/openclaw-gateway-switch 2>&1 || echo \"脚本不存在\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 检查 Gateway 服务 ===\"\nopenclaw gateway status 2>&1 | head -15","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":73190,"output":227,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73417,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775790675693,"responseId":"chatcmpl-af16711c-63da-48da-b90e-1a2df0e74dac"}}
