{"type":"message","id":"4d785b2f","parentId":"e357e95e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:13:12.300Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 11:13 GMT+8] 看一看，回答我：1. 释放 3101 端口（为 Gateway 腾位置）\nbash\n# 停止占用 3101 的旧进程（可能是旧的 context-api 或 router）\nfuser -k 3101/tcp\n# 确认端口已释放\nss -tlnp | grep 3101\n2. 修改 Gateway 端口为 3101（通过 systemd）\nGateway 由 systemd 管理，需修改其启动参数。\n\nbash\n# 编辑 Gateway 的服务文件\nsudo systemctl edit openclaw-gateway.service\n在打开的编辑器中添加以下内容（如果已有 [Service] 段则追加在其后）：\n\ntext\n[Service]\nEnvironment=\"OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=3101\"\n# 或者直接修改启动命令（视实际服务文件而定）\nExecStart=\nExecStart=/usr/bin/openclaw gateway --port 3101\n保存后重载并重启：\n\nbash\nsudo systemctl daemon-reload\nsudo systemctl restart openclaw-gateway.service\n验证 Gateway 是否在新端口运行：\n\nbash\ncurl http://localhost:3101/health\n3. 停止原 3102 上的旧服务\nbash\n# 查找并停止占用 3102 的进程（可能是旧 router 或残留 Gateway）\nfuser -k 3102/tcp\n4. 让代理接管 3102\n修改代理的 .env 或配置，确保监听 3102，并指向新的 Gateway WebSocket 地址。\n\nbash\ncd ~/.openclaw/proxy\n# 编辑 .env，设置：\n# PROXY_PORT=3102\n# GATEWAY_WS_URL=ws://localhost:3101/ws\n启动/重启代理：\n\nbash\npm2 restart openclaw-proxy || pm2 start index.js --name openclaw-proxy\npm2 save\n验证代理已在 3102 运行：\n\nbash\nss -tlnp | grep 3102 # 应显示 node 进程\ncurl http://localhost:3102/health\n5. 浏览器测试\n访问 http://localhost:3102/chat，界面应原样呈现，发送消息后观察 Network 请求是否发往 3102，并验证功能正常。\n\n回退预案（如遇 UI 异常或消息无响应）\nbash\n# 停止代理\npm2 stop openclaw-proxy\n\n# 恢复 Gateway 到 3102\nsudo systemctl edit openclaw-gateway.service # 移除端口环境变量或改回 3102\nsudo systemctl daemon-reload\nsudo systemctl restart openclaw-gateway.service"}],"timestamp":1775790792287}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7bfea38","parentId":"4d785b2f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:13:15.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提供了一个更详细的方案，需要我检查可行性。让我分析：\n\n1. 释放 3101 端口 - 需要先停止旧进程\n2. 修改 Gateway 端口为 3101 - 需要用 systemctl，但用户之前显示 Gateway 运行在 3108，是 systemd 管理的\n3. 停止 3102 上的旧服务 - 需要停掉旧 router\n4. 代理接管 3102 - 修改配置并重启\n5. 测试\n\n问题是：\n- 用户环境可能没有 sudo 权限\n- systemctl 命令可能需要 root 权限\n\n让我检查一下当前状态和权限。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1ffb410f688c43b28e0a7809","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查当前端口和进程\necho \"=== 当前端口 ===\"\nss -tlnp | grep -E \"3101|3102|3108\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 检查 3108 Gateway 进程 ===\"\nps aux | grep \"openclaw-gateway\" | grep -v grep | head -2\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 检查是否用 systemd 管理 ===\"\nsystemctl status openclaw-gateway.service 2>&1 | head -5","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":74344,"output":250,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74594,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775790792320,"responseId":"chatcmpl-12bbaa3e-9bcf-4d0b-ac75-7f99a4cbf86d"}}
