{"type":"message","id":"42384845","parentId":"770ccad8","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:13:18.921Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"分析：\n\n1. **Gateway 在 3108**，进程名是 `openclaw-gateway`，是 user systemd 管理（不是 system）\n2. **3102 被旧 router 占用**\n3. **3101 被旧 context-api 占用**\n\n用户提供的方案需要 `sudo systemctl`，但这是 user systemd，不是 system-wide。\n\n让我检查用户的 systemd 服务：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_87ab79d95fff4d8a9f7669d7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 user systemd 服务\nsystemctl --user status openclaw-gateway 2>&1 | head -8\n\necho \"\"\n# 检查服务文件位置\ncat ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service 2>/dev/null | head -15","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":74841,"output":159,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75000,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775790795393,"responseId":"chatcmpl-237882b9-2ef2-4ae9-aa69-ad519d8d47be"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d723b9e","parentId":"42384845","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:13:19.019Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_87ab79d95fff4d8a9f7669d7","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"● openclaw-gateway.service - OpenClaw Gateway (v2026.3.13)\n     Loaded: loaded (/home/ai/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service; enabled; vendor preset: enabled)\n     Active: active (running) since Fri 2026-04-10 10:40:28 CST; 32min ago\n   Main PID: 11352 (openclaw-gatewa)\n      Tasks: 38 (limit: 21572)\n     Memory: 597.4M\n        CPU: 1min 23.773s\n     CGroup: /user.slice/user-1000.slice/user@1000.service/openclaw-gateway.service\n\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Gateway (v2026.3.13)\nAfter=network-online.target\nWants=network-online.target\n\n[Service]\nExecStart=/usr/bin/node /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 3108\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nTimeoutStopSec=30\nTimeoutStartSec=30\nSuccessExitStatus=0 143\nKillMode=control-group\nEnvironment=HOME=/home/ai\nEnvironment=TMPDIR=/tmp"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":53,"aggregated":"● openclaw-gateway.service - OpenClaw Gateway (v2026.3.13)\n     Loaded: loaded (/home/ai/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service; enabled; vendor preset: enabled)\n     Active: active (running) since Fri 2026-04-10 10:40:28 CST; 32min ago\n   Main PID: 11352 (openclaw-gatewa)\n      Tasks: 38 (limit: 21572)\n     Memory: 597.4M\n        CPU: 1min 23.773s\n     CGroup: /user.slice/user-1000.slice/user@1000.service/openclaw-gateway.service\n\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Gateway (v2026.3.13)\nAfter=network-online.target\nWants=network-online.target\n\n[Service]\nExecStart=/usr/bin/node /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 3108\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nTimeoutStopSec=30\nTimeoutStartSec=30\nSuccessExitStatus=0 143\nKillMode=control-group\nEnvironment=HOME=/ho