{"type":"message","id":"57f9f3a1","parentId":"4535e313","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:15:00.598Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要确认方案的每一步，准备回答用户。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 方案评估 ✅\n\n**可以执行**，步骤清晰。\n\n| 步骤 | 操作 | 确认 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 释放 3101, 3102 | `fuser -k` 即可 |\n| 2 | Gateway → 3101 | 改 service 文件 + reload |\n| 3 | 代理 → 3102 | 改 .env + 重启 |\n| 4 | 验证 | 访问 3102/chat |\n\n**唯一要注意**：\n- 代理的 GATEWAY_WS_URL 需要改成 `ws://localhost:3101/ws`\n- 当前 .env 缺少 GATEWAY_WS_URL 配置\n\n---\n\n**确认执行吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":76029,"output":165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76194,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775790897216,"responseId":"chatcmpl-daa30805-88d7-485e-b121-193e8074b0c9"}}
