{"type":"message","id":"c6f7b663","parentId":"0974a6d9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:16:23.130Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 11:16 GMT+8] 再看看，回答我：第一步：备份关键文件\nbash\n# 备份 Gateway 服务文件\ncp ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service.bak\n\n# 备份代理环境变量\ncp ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env.bak\n第二步：释放 3101 和 3102 端口\nbash\nfuser -k 3101/tcp\nfuser -k 3102/tcp\nss -tlnp | grep -E \"3101|3102\" # 应无输出\n第三步：修改 Gateway 服务端口为 3101\nbash\n# 编辑服务文件\nnano ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service\n找到 ExecStart 行，将 --port 3108 改为 --port 3101（若无显式端口则追加 --port 3101）。\n保存后重载并重启：\n\nbash\nsystemctl --user daemon-reload\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway.service\n验证 Gateway 已在新端口运行：\n\nbash\ncurl http://localhost:3101/health\n第四步：配置代理并接管 3102\nbash\ncd ~/.openclaw/proxy\n\n# 更新 .env：监听 3102，并指定 WebSocket 后端为 Gateway:3101\ncat > .env << 'EOF'\nPROXY_PORT=3102\nCLASSIFIER_URL=http://localhost:3104/classify\nSCORER_URL=http://localhost:3103/api/score\nV8_TASK_API=http://localhost:3103/api/task\nGATEWAY_WS_URL=ws://localhost:3101/ws\nBYPASS_MODE=false\nEOF\n\n# 重启代理\npm2 restart openclaw-proxy || pm2 start index.js --name openclaw-proxy\npm2 save\n验证代理已监听 3102：\n\nbash\nss -tlnp | grep 3102 # 应显示 node 进程\ncurl http://localhost:3102/health\n第五步：浏览器验证\n访问 http://localhost:3102/chat，界面应原样呈现。发送测试消息（例如“帮我分析代码质量”），观察返回是否包含任务 ID。\n\n回退预案（若出现问题）\nbash\n# 停止代理\npm2 stop openclaw-proxy\n\n# 恢复 Gateway 服务文件\ncp ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service.bak ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service\nsystemctl --user daemon-reload\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway.service\n\n# 恢复代理 .env（可选）\ncp ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env.bak ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env\npm2 restart openclaw-proxy"}],"timestamp":1775790983118}}
