{"type":"message","id":"06d9042c","parentId":"cc0730aa","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:16:40.183Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，确认了当前 Gateway 确实是用 --port 3108 启动的。这个方案可以执行。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 方案完全可行 ✅\n\n**确认当前状态**：\n- Gateway 用 `systemd --user` 管理\n- 启动命令：`gateway --port 3108`\n- 代理配置在 `~/.openclaw/proxy/.env`\n\n---\n\n**完整步骤**：\n\n1. 备份\n2. 杀端口 3101, 3102\n3. 改 service: 3108 → 3101\n4. reload + restart Gateway\n5. 写代理 .env (3102 + ws://3101)\n6. 重启代理\n7. 验证\n\n---\n\n**要做吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":75713,"output":151,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77016,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775790985297,"responseId":"019d756373916465ca9ef5ecede75464"}}
