{"type":"message","id":"f4383e69","parentId":"757d1419","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:20:46.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"3102 上有 HTTP 服务，返回了 health 和 HTML。看起来 router (13839) 仍在运行并且提供网页服务。\n\n这说明虽然我们尝试迁移，但实际上 3102 还是原来的 router 在服务。\n\n用户说\"我现在就在3102\"，意味着他能访问网页。这意味着：\n1. 原 router 仍在 3102 运行\n2. 迁移没有真正完成\n\n让我确认一下。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 3102 现状\n\n**3102 仍被 router 占用**，提供网页服务。\n\n```\ncurl localhost:3102 → 返回 Gateway 样式的 HTML\n```\n\n这说明：\n- **迁移没有完成**\n- 原 router 仍在 3102 运行\n- 用户能访问的是**旧版**（没有分类评分）\n\n---\n\n**如果要实现智能分类，需要**：\n1. 杀掉 3102 的 router\n2. 启动代理到 3102\n\n要继续执行迁移吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":81024,"output":186,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81210,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775798442790,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4d752084-52f7-4e24-9fe9-11a1f69fa702"}}
