{"type":"message","id":"44512586","parentId":"00f7225f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:22:47.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户需要回退预案。让我整理一个安全的回退步骤。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 回退预案\n\n**目标**：恢复到迁移前的状态\n\n### 步骤\n\n```bash\n# 1. 恢复 service 文件\ncp ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service.bak ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service\n\n# 2. 杀掉所有旧进程\nfuser -k 3101/tcp 3102/tcp 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 3. 重载并重启 Gateway\nsystemctl --user daemon-reload\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway.service\n\n# 4. 恢复代理配置\ncp ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env.bak ~/.openclaw/proxy/.env\n\n# 5. 验证\nss -tlnp | grep 3102\ncurl http://localhost:3102/health\n```\n\n---\n\n**恢复到**：\n- Gateway → 3108（原始）\n- 3102 → 原 router\n- 代理 → 3105（原始配置）\n\n要做吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":80172,"output":221,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81545,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775798547967,"responseId":"019d75d770bde4f1bcdd50ad5547ecf1"}}
