{"type":"message","id":"62094f25","parentId":"1e162461","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:26:20.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说 3105 太垃圾了，可能是在说代理的响应不对。之前测试的结果是：\n- 闲聊 \"你好\" → 返回模板 \"你好！有什么技术问题需要帮助？\"\n- \"测试\" → 返回 \"收到，clarify\"\n\n但用户可能期望的是像 3102 那样的完整网页体验。让我问问用户具体是什么问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**3105 的问题**：\n- 没有完整的网页 UI（只有简单的 chat.html）\n- 功能不完整\n\n---\n\n**当前最好的选择**：\n\n**继续用 3102**（原来的 Gateway 网页），功能稳定完整。\n\n**3105 可以作为备选**，或者不管它。\n\n你想怎么处理？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":84672,"output":137,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775798777453,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0d6a7340-fb78-4960-94b4-67683b4eae6d"}}
