{"type":"message","id":"d46e834b","parentId":"4f247cc8","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:42:45.768Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"结果：\n- Gateway 3108: ✅ 正常\n- 分类器 3104: ✅ 正常\n- 评分 3103: ❌ 有问题（返回 HTML 而不是 JSON）\n- 3102: 被占用\n\n需要：\n1. 修复 3103（启动 v8）\n2. 释放 3102 端口\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 第一步结果\n\n| 服务 | 状态 | 问题 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Gateway 3108 | ✅ | 正常 |\n| 分类器 3104 | ✅ | 正常 |\n| 评分 3103 | ❌ | 需要启动 |\n| 3102 | 被占用 | router 进程 |\n\n需要：\n1. 启动 3103 评分服务\n2. 杀掉 3102 的 router\n\n继续吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":86574,"output":171,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86745,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775799762354,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3c266249-38e0-421a-addd-e27d891d0f8a"}}
