{"type":"message","id":"76e70c8a","parentId":"eda57e65","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:48:58.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问准备怎么升级。让我按照之前学习方案的步骤来回答。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 升级步骤（按方案）\n\n### 第一步：确认 3102 空闲\n```bash\n# 杀掉 3102 的 router\nfuser -k 3102/tcp\n```\n\n### 第二步：配置代理 .env\n```\nPROXY_PORT=3102\nGATEWAY_TARGET=http://localhost:3108\nGATEWAY_WS_URL=ws://localhost:3108\n```\n\n### 第三步：添加转发中间件\n代理需要把 `/chat` 和 WebSocket 转发到 Gateway 3108\n\n### 第四步：启动代理在 3102\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/proxy\nnode index.js\n```\n\n### 结果\n- 3102 网页 UI → 代理 → 分类(3104) → 评分(3103) → Gateway(3108)\n\n---\n\n**关键**：代理需要能转发网页请求到 3108，否则 UI 会丢失。\n\n需要我先修改代理代码加入转发功能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":622,"output":217,"cacheRead":86784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87623,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775800127412,"responseId":"019d75ef825d14a3ac9b0c8400e1f139"}}
