{"type":"message","id":"48f33b23","parentId":"0dbe3a45","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:21:16.594Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d760d31d205e34622d02957931a56","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"app.post('/api/chat/send', async (req, res) => {\n  const { message, context = {} } = req.body;\n  if (!message) return res.status(400).json({ error: 'message is required' });\n\n  // 添加用户消息到上下文\n  await addContextMessage('user', message);\n\n  if (bypass) {\n    try {\n      const gwRes = await axios.post(`${GATEWAY_URL}/api/chat/send`, req.body, { timeout: 30000 });\n      return res.json(gwRes.data);"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":58,"aggregated":"app.post('/api/chat/send', async (req, res) => {\n  const { message, context = {} } = req.body;\n  if (!message) return res.status(400).json({ error: 'message is required' });\n\n  // 添加用户消息到上下文\n  await addContextMessage('user', message);\n\n  if (bypass) {\n    try {\n      const gwRes = await axios.post(`${GATEWAY_URL}/api/chat/send`, req.body, { timeout: 30000 });\n      return res.json(gwRes.data);","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775802076577}}
{"type":"message","id":"8a21d496","parentId":"48f33b23","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:21:19.824Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我看完整的处理逻辑。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 顺序：先分类，后评分\n\n```\n消息 → 分类(3104) → 判断是否任务 \n              ↓ 是任务 → 评分(3103) → 执行\n              ↓ 非任务 → 直接返回\n```\n\n**代码逻辑**：\n1. 先调用 `classify(message)` - 分类\n2. 如果 `isTask: true`，再调用 `score(message, context)` - 评分\n\n所以：\n- **闲聊/提问** → 分类 → 判定非任务 → **不需要评分**\n- **任务指令** → 分类 → 判定任务 → **才评分**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":105855,"output":132,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105987,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775802076598,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d4bf5c12-b6e5-4030-bc0e-a8b9f4dc26c7"}}
