{"type":"message","id":"0c138b76","parentId":"53f7fd24","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:28:44.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要了解所有技能的用途和推荐。让我查看一些关键技能的 SKILL.md 来了解它们的功能。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d761335f4d554eac91cf8e5c05e40","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 关键技能功能说明 ===\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"--- 1. v8_classifier (已启用) ---\"\ngrep \"description\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/manifest.json\n\necho \"\"\necho \"--- 2. v8_scorer (已启用) ---\"\ngrep \"description\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_scorer/manifest.json\n\necho \"\"\necho \"--- 3. ontology ---\"\nhead -20 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ontology/SKILL.md | grep -A5 \"description\\|When to use\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"--- 4. intent-enhancer ---\"\ngrep \"触发词\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/intent-enhancer/SKILL.md\n\necho \"\"\necho \"--- 5. memory-keeper ---\"\nhead -10 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/memory-keeper/SKILL.md\n\necho \"\"\necho \"--- 6. proactivity ---\"\ngrep \"description\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/proactivity/SKILL.md | head -1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"--- 7. self-improving ---\"\ngrep \"description\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving/SKILL.md | head -1","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1793,"output":315,"cacheRead":105856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107964,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775802502861,"responseId":"019d76132599f35d5b1a02648be42c4d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e62c7029","parentId":"0c138b76","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:28:45.051Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d761335f4d554eac91cf8e5c05e40","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 关键技能功能说明 ===\n\n--- 1. v8_classifier (已启用) ---\n  \"description\": \"调用 v8 场景分类服务，识别用户意图\",\n\n--- 2. v8_scorer (已启用) ---\n  \"description\": \"调用 v8 评分引擎，评估任务复杂度\",\n\n--- 3. ontology ---\ndescription: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\n---\n\n# Ontology\n\nA typed vocabulary + constraint system for representing knowledge as a verifiable graph.\n\n--- 4. intent-enhancer ---\ndescription: 增强意图检测识别隐式任务，包括故障类、问题描述类关键词和正则模式匹配。触发词：故障/卡顿/异常等问题识别。\n## 触发词\n\n--- 5. memory-keeper ---\n# Memory Keeper Agent\n\n> 自动化记忆维护 Agent\n\n## 用途\n\n定期整理和优化长期记忆系统。\n\n## 核心职责\n\n\n--- 6. proactivity ---\ndescription: Anticipates needs, keeps work moving, and improves through use so the agent gets more proactive over time.\n\n--- 7. self-improving ---\ndescription: \"Self-reflection + Self-criticism + Self-learning + Self-organizing memory. Agent evaluates its own work, catches mistakes, and improves permanently. Use when (1) a command, tool, API, or operation fails; (2) the user corrects you or rejects your work; (3) you realize your knowledge is outdated or incorrect; (4) you discover a better approach; (5) the user explicitly installs or references the skill for the current task.\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":52,"aggregated":"=== 关键技能功能说明 ===\n\n--- 1. v8_classifier (已启用) ---\n  \"description\": \"调用 v8 场景分类服务，识别用户意图\",\n\n--- 2. v8_scorer (已启用) ---\n  \"description\": \"调用 v8 评分引擎，评估任务复杂度\",\n\n--- 3. ontology ---\ndescription: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\n---\n\n# Ontology\n\nA typed vocabulary + constraint system for representing knowledge as a verifiable graph.\n\n--- 4. intent-enhancer ---\ndescription: 增强意图检测识别隐式任务，包括故障类、问题描述类关键词和正则模式匹配。触发词：故障/卡顿/异常等问题识别。\n## 触发词\n\n--- 5. memory-keeper ---\n# Memory Keeper Agent\n\n> 自动化记忆维护 Agent\n\n## 用途\n\n定期整理和优化长期记忆系统。\n\n## 核心职责\n\n\n--- 6. proactivity ---\ndescription: Anticipates needs, keeps work moving, and improves through use so the agent gets more proactive over time.\n\n--- 7. self-improving ---\ndescription: \"Self-reflection + Self-criticism + Self-learning + Self-organizing memory. Agent evaluates its own work, catches mistakes, and improves permanently. Use when (1) a command, tool, API, or operation fails; (2) the user corrects you or rejects your work; (3) you realize your knowledge is outdated or incorrect; (4) you discover a better approach; (5) the user explicitly installs or references the skill for the current task.\"","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775802525038}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef6153ae","parentId":"e62c7029","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:28:49.414Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我总结一下这些技能的用途和推荐。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 技能功能总结\n\n### ✅ 已启用\n\n| 技能 | 功能 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| v8_classifier | 场景分类 | 识别用户意图（闲聊/任务/故障） |\n| v8_scorer | 任务评分 | 评估任务复杂度 + 推荐执行策略 |\n\n---\n\n### 📋 可选技能推荐\n\n| 技能 | 功能 | 推荐度 | 说明 |\n|------|------|--------|------|\n| **ontology** | 知识图谱 | ⭐⭐⭐ | 结构化记忆，查询实体关系 |\n| **intent-enhancer** | 意图增强 | ⭐⭐ | 增强隐式任务识别 |\n| **memory-keeper** | 记忆维护 | ⭐⭐ | 自动清理/整理记忆（定时任务） |\n| **proactivity** | 主动增强 | ⭐⭐ | 预测需求，主动推进 |\n| **self-improving** | 自我改进 | ⭐⭐⭐ | 错误反思，持续学习 |\n| elite-longterm-memory | 长期记忆 | ⭐⭐ | 向量搜索 + 持久化 |\n\n---\n\n### 推荐\n\n**当前已启用**的 v8_classifier + v8_scorer 已满足核心需求。\n\n**可额外启用**：\n1. **self-improving** - 有助于持续改进\n2. **ontology** - 结构化记忆\n3. **intent-enhancer** - 增强意图识别（与 v8_classifier 互补）\n\n要启用这些吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":108447,"output":323,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108770,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775802525057,"responseId":"chatcmpl-43992a4c-6c1d-41a5-b0d9-662766e0e353"}}
