{"type":"message","id":"e4c61c3a","parentId":"b15670c0","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:30:02.480Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6f1f1561cf8846959335ac5e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OpenClaw Workspace\n\nThis is the workspace for OpenClaw AI assistant.\n\n## 核心规则\n\n### 消息预处理：场景分类 + 任务评分\n\n收到用户消息时，按以下流程处理：\n\n**第一步：场景分类** - 调用 `v8_classifier` skill\n- 分类服务：`http://localhost:3104/classify`\n- 场景标签：task_multi_step, fault_recovery, chitchat, vague_request, novice_user, expert_user, high_risk_automated, task_status_query, cancel_task\n\n**第二步：根据场景处理**\n- `chitchat` → 直接 LLM 回应\n- `fault_recovery` → 故障恢复模板\n- `vague_request` → 澄清意图\n- `novice_user` → 带解释的入门指南\n- `expert_user` → 直接给要点\n- 其他场景 → 继续评分\n\n**第三步：任务评分** - 调用 `v8_scorer` skill（仅任务类型）\n- 评分服务：`http://localhost:3103/api/score`\n- 6 因子评分：logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, dependency\n\n**第四步：策略路由**\n\n根据评分结果选择执行策略：\n\n| 分数 | 策略 | 超时 | 内存限制 |\n|------|------|------|----------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s | - |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s | 1024MB |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s | 2048MB |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s | 2048MB |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s | 8192MB |\n\n---\n\n### 旧版意图判断（已废弃，用 v8_classifier 替代）\n\n~~**第一步：意图判断** (`POST /api/intent`)\n- 判断用户消息是否是任务~~\n\n---\n\n### 任务执行前必做：意图判断 + 复杂度评估\n\n~~**第一步：意图判断** (`POST /api/intent`)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":45,"aggregated":"# OpenClaw Workspace\n\nThis is the workspace for OpenClaw AI assistant.\n\n## 核心规则\n\n### 消息预处理：场景分类 + 任务评分\n\n收到用户消息时，按以下流程处理：\n\n**第一步：场景分类** - 调用 `v8_classifier` skill\n- 分类服务：`http://localhost:3104/classify`\n- 场景标签：task_multi_step, fault_recovery, chitchat, vague_request, novice_user, expert_user, high_risk_automated, task_status_query, cancel_task\n\n**第二步：根据场景处理**\n- `chitchat` → 直接 LLM 回应\n- `fault_recovery` → 故障恢复模板\n- `vague_request` → 澄清意图\n- `novice_user` → 带解释的入门指南\n- `expert_user` → 直接给要点\n- 其他场景 → 继续评分\n\n**第三步：任务评分** - 调用 `v8_scorer` skill（仅任务类型）\n- 评分服务：`http://localhost:3103/api/score`\n- 6 因子评分：logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, dependency\n\n**第四步：策略路由**\n\n根据评分结果选择执行策略：\n\n| 分数 | 策略 | 超时 | 内存限制 |\n|------|------|------|----------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s | - |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s | 1024MB |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s | 2048MB |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s | 2048MB |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s | 8192MB |\n\n---\n\n### 旧版意图判断（已废弃，用 v8_classifier 替代）\n\n~~**第一步：意图判断** (`POST /api/intent`)\n- 判断用户消息是否是任务~~\n\n---\n\n### 任务执行前必做：意图判断 + 复杂度评估\n\n~~**第一步：意图判断** (`POST /api/intent`)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775802602470}}
{"type":"message","id":"f108020b","parentId":"e4c61c3a","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:30:12.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我总结 OpenClaw 的核心能力。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## OpenClaw 自身能力\n\n### 核心处理流程（已实现）\n\n| 阶段 | 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **1. 场景分类** | v8_classifier (3104) | ✅ |\n| **2. 意图判断** | task_multi_step, chitchat, fault_recovery 等 | ✅ |\n| **3. 任务评分** | v8_scorer (3103) 6因子评分 | ✅ |\n| **4. 策略路由** | DIRECT / SUBAGENT / PARALLEL / MEGA | ✅ |\n\n### 内置能力\n\n| 能力 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **模型调用** | codingplan/minimax-m2.5 |\n| **上下文管理** | memory-core 插件，已启用 |\n| **任务编排** | task_orchestrator v3.0 |\n| **执行策略** | DIRECT / STEP / SUBAGENT / PARALLEL |\n| **安全拦截** | CRITICAL 级别硬拦截 |\n| **进程管理** | 支持子代理、后台任务 |\n\n### 当前工作流\n\n```\n用户消息 → 3102 代理 → 分类(3104) → 评分(3103) → 路由 → 执行\n                                   ↓\n                            Gateway(3108) → LLM\n```\n\n**你现在就生活在完整的框架中**，分类评分都已在 3102 入口自动处理。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":110033,"output":309,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110342,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775802602487,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e7094dc1-192d-4755-b5bc-c453c4e81d24"}}
