{"type":"message","id":"6e9bbe64","parentId":"cbff4672","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:33:03.507Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d7617f77b79fe100c27b1bf6c291b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== v8 核心模块功能 ===\n1. scoring (评分引擎):\nadapter.js\nadapter.js.bak\nengine.js\nscoring.js\n\n2. executor (执行器):\nExecutionGuard.js\nSandboxExecutor.js\n\n3. scheduler (调度器):\nScheduler.js\n\n4. router (路由):\napi.js"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":56,"aggregated":"=== v8 核心模块功能 ===\n1. scoring (评分引擎):\nadapter.js\nadapter.js.bak\nengine.js\nscoring.js\n\n2. executor (执行器):\nExecutionGuard.js\nSandboxExecutor.js\n\n3. scheduler (调度器):\nScheduler.js\n\n4. router (路由):\napi.js","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775802783494}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5f1e3c1","parentId":"6e9bbe64","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:33:26.655Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我给用户一个完整的 v8 任务编排器状态总结。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## v8 任务编排器状态\n\n### 核心模块（已实现）\n\n| 模块 | 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **scoring** | 6因子评分引擎 (logic/risk/duration/resource/uncertainty/dependency) | ✅ 运行中 3103 |\n| **executor** | 执行器 (SandboxExecutor, ExecutionGuard) | ✅ |\n| **scheduler** | 任务调度器 | ✅ |\n| **router** | API 路由 | ✅ |\n| **skills** | 技能加载器 | ✅ (含 auto_improve) |\n\n---\n\n### 当前流程\n\n```\n3102 代理 → 分类(3104) → 评分(3103) → 任务编排器\n                                      ↓\n                              DIRECT / STEP_ARCHIVE / SUBAGENT / PARALLEL\n```\n\n---\n\n### 评测结果示例\n\n```json\n{\"score\":33,\"recommendedStrategy\":\"STEP_ARCHIVE\",\"timeout\":60}\n```\n\n- 评分：33分\n- 策略：STEP_ARCHIVE\n- 超时：60秒\n\n**v8 任务编排器已在运行**，分类后会根据评分自动选择执行策略。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":110759,"output":257,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112168,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775802783513,"responseId":"019d76180d3ad7f7348399190aa31b3f"}}
