{"type":"message","id":"b7792f71","parentId":"dcb2cdd4","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:40:21.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我对照文档给出一个完整的对比报告。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 对照文档检查结果\n\n### ✅ 已实现\n\n| 模块 | 文档要求 | 实际状态 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| **v8 核心** | 12个模块 | ✅ config/context/executor/observability/persistence/router/scheduler/scoring/security/skills/utils |\n| **评分引擎** | 6因子+组合规则 | ✅ adapter.js, engine.js, scoring.js |\n| **分类器** | 9种场景分类 | ✅ api_server.py, feedback/collector.py |\n| **代理服务** | 统一入口+转发+WS | ✅ index.js, http-proxy-middleware |\n| **上下文API** | Token监控+压缩 | ✅ index.js 有 compressContext |\n| **auto_improve** | 6模块 | ✅ goalParser/snapshot/evaluator/planner/executor/autoImprove |\n\n### ❌ 缺失/未实现\n\n| 模块 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **rule-tuner.js** | 评分规则自动调优工具 |\n| **weight-learner.js** | 评分权重自适应学习 |\n| **strategy-analyzer.js** | 策略分析报告生成器 |\n| **分类器热更新** | `/reload-rules` API |\n| **监控告警** | 缺少自动告警集成 |\n\n### 建议补全\n\n1. **rule-tuner.js** - 基于历史任务自动调整评分阈值\n2. **热更新 API** - 分类器规则热加载\n3. **策略分析脚本** - 定期生成报告\n\n需要实现这些缺失模块吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":117083,"output":338,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118573,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775803192046,"responseId":"019d761da3a667caac5aaaa414551c53"}}
