{"type":"message","id":"794d237e","parentId":"dc7c5bd9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:46:18.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"热更新端点现在正常工作了。让我总结一下实现的内容。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 实现完成\n\n### 新增模块\n\n| 模块 | 路径 | 功能 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **rule-tuner.js** | `~/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/` | 基于历史任务自动调整评分阈值 |\n| **weight-learner.js** | `~/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/` | 基于用户反馈调整因子权重 |\n| **strategy-analyzer.js** | `~/.openclaw/v8/src/observability/` | 生成策略分析报告 (markdown) |\n| **热更新 API** | 3104 `/reload-rules`, `/update-rules`, `/rules` | 动态更新分类规则 |\n\n### 使用方法\n\n```bash\n# 评分规则调优\ncd ~/.openclaw/v8\nnode src/scoring/rule-tuner.js --config config/tuner.yaml --output tuning_report.json\n\n# 权重自适应学习\nnode src/scoring/weight-learner.js --db ./data/tasks.db --output config/weights.json\n\n# 策略分析报告\nnode src/observability/strategy-analyzer.js --days 7 --output report.md\n\n# 分类器热更新\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3104/reload-rules  # 重载规则\ncurl -X GET http://localhost:3104/rules           # 获取当前规则\n```\n\n### 验证\n\n```\n热更新 API 测试: ✅\n{\"task_keywords\":[\"帮我\",\"请\",\"做\",...]}\n```\n\n现在所有缺失模块都已实现！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":128459,"output":323,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128782,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775803571440,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3ac1c97d-5a60-46b4-ba5f-afcd40c5b70b"}}
