{"type":"message","id":"b7c400fc","parentId":"c666f71c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:06:37.043Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 15:05 GMT+8] 学习：代理 systemd 服务 (P1)\n创建用户级 systemd 服务，实现代理开机自启和崩溃重启。\n\nbash\ncat > ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-proxy.service << 'EOF'\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Proxy (v8 enhanced)\nAfter=network.target openclaw-gateway.service\nWants=openclaw-gateway.service\n\n[Service]\nWorkingDirectory=/home/ai/.openclaw/proxy\nExecStart=/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node index.js\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nTimeoutStopSec=10\nEnvironment=NODE_ENV=production\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=default.target\nEOF\n\nsystemctl --user daemon-reload\nsystemctl --user enable openclaw-proxy.service\nsystemctl --user start openclaw-proxy.service\n验证：\n\nbash\nsystemctl --user status openclaw-proxy.service\ncurl http://localhost:3102/health\n分类器自动重训练检查脚本 (P0)\n创建 check_retrain.py，用于检测低置信样本数量并触发重训练。\n\nbash\ncat > ~/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/scripts/check_retrain.py << 'EOF'\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"检查是否需要重新训练分类器\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport argparse\n\ndef count_low_confidence(log_file, threshold=0.5):\n \"\"\"统计低置信度和歧义样本数\"\"\"\n if not os.path.exists(log_file):\n print(f\"日志文件 {log_file} 不存在\")\n return 0\n count = 0\n with open(log_file, 'r') as f:\n for line in f:\n try:\n event = json.loads(line)\n if event.get('meta') in ('low_confidence', 'ambiguous'):\n if event.get('confidence', 0) < threshold:\n count += 1\n except:\n pass\n return count\n\ndef main():\n parser = argparse.ArgumentParser()\n parser.add_argument('--threshold', type=int, default=50, help='触发重训练的样本数阈值')\n parser.add_argument('--log-file', default='logs/meta_events.jsonl')\n parser.add_argument('--auto', action='store_true', help='自动执行重训练')\n args = parser.parse_args()\n\n count = count_low_confidence(args.log_file)\n print(f\"低置信样本数: {count}\")\n\n if count >= args.threshold:\n print(f\"达到阈值 {args.threshold}，需要重训练\")\n if args.auto:\n os.system('python scripts/train_classifier.py')\n sys.exit(0)\n else:\n print(f\"未达阈值，无需重训练\")\n sys.exit(1)\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n main()\nEOF\n\nchmod +x ~/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/scripts/check_retrain.py\n验证：\n\nbash\ncd ~/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier\npython scripts/check_retrain.py --threshold 50"}],"timestamp":1775804797032}}
