{"type":"message","id":"4544f2a5","parentId":"d8915ddb","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:08:46.374Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来有多个启动方式，实际运行的是：\n1. 3102 代理: `/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js`（可能是符号链接到 proxy/index.js）\n2. 3103 v8: `cd ~/.openclaw/v8 && node src/index.js`3. 3104 分类器: `python3 api_server.py`4. 3106: 需要检查\n\n让我检查 openclaw-router 是否是符号链接，然后创建正确的 systemd 服务。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6ea61018d84c43ad8be9eb06","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查是否是符号链接\necho \"=== 检查符号链接 ===\"\nls -la /home/ai/openclaw-router 2>/dev/null || echo \"不是符号链接\"\n\necho \"\"\n# 为每个服务创建 systemd 文件\n\n# 1. 3102 代理服务\ncat > ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-proxy.service << 'EOF'\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Proxy (3102 - v8 enhanced)\nAfter=network.target openclaw-gateway.service\nWants=openclaw-gateway.service\n\n[Service]\nWorkingDirectory=/home/ai/.openclaw/proxy\nExecStart=/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node index.js\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nTimeoutStopSec=10\nEnvironment=NODE_ENV=production\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=default.target\nEOF\n\n# 2. 3103 v8 评分服务\ncat > ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-v8.service << 'EOF'\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw v8 Task Orchestrator (3103)\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nWorkingDirectory=/home/ai/.openclaw/v8\nExecStart=/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node src/index.js\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nTimeoutStopSec=10\nEnvironment=NODE_ENV=production\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=default.target\nEOF\n\n# 3. 3104 场景分类器\ncat > ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-classifier.service << 'EOF'\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Scene Classifier (3104)\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nWorkingDirectory=/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier\nExecStart=/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier/venv/bin/python api_server.py\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nTimeoutStopSec=10\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=default.target