{"type":"message","id":"2afde597","parentId":"24a52d36","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:08:54.615Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"原来 openclaw-router 是一个独立的目录，和 ~/.openclaw/proxy/ 是不同的。openclaw-router 有自己的 openclaw-router.js。让我检查实际的运行命令，然后正确更新服务文件。\n\n实际运行的 3102 代理是 `/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js`。我需要更新服务文件来指向正确的路径。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3f3fa88305594491a013cacf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 更新 3102 代理服务路径为实际的\ncat > ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-proxy.service << 'EOF'\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Proxy (3102 - v8 enhanced)\nAfter=network.target openclaw-gateway.service\nWants=openclaw-gateway.service\n\n[Service]\nWorkingDirectory=/home/ai/openclaw-router\nExecStart=/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node openclaw-router.js\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nTimeoutStopSec=10\nEnvironment=NODE_ENV=production\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=default.target\nEOF\n\n# 更新 3106 服务\ncat > ~/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-context-api.service << 'EOF'\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Context API (3106)\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nWorkingDirectory=/home/ai/openclaw-listener\nExecStart=/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node dist/main.js\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nTimeoutStopSec=10\nEnvironment=NODE_ENV=production\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=default.target\nEOF\n\n# 重新加载 systemd\nsystemctl --user daemon-reload\n\necho \"=== 启用所有服务 ===\"\nsystemctl --user enable openclaw-proxy.service\nsystemctl --user enable openclaw-v8.service\nsystemctl --user enable openclaw-classifier.service\nsystemctl --user enable openclaw-context-api.service\nsystemctl --user enable openclaw-gateway.service\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 服务状态 ===\"\nsystemctl --user list-unit-files --type=service | grep openclaw","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":62162,"output":452,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWri