{"type":"message","id":"28f42f5c","parentId":"df34e125","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:47:00.334Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"检查结果显示框架基本完整。我来总结一下可以增强的地方。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 框架状态总结\n\n### ✅ 已完成\n\n| 模块 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| v8 评分引擎 + 6因子 | ✅ |\n| 评分增强 (rule-tuner, weight-learner) | ✅ |\n| 策略分析 (strategy-analyzer) | ✅ |\n| 分类器自迭代 (check_retrain) | ✅ |\n| 分类器热更新 API | ✅ |\n| systemd 自启 (7个服务) | ✅ |\n| 技能启用 (6+2) | ✅ |\n| Soul v9.4 | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### 🟡 可选增强项\n\n| 项目 | 说明 | 优先级 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| **3101 旧服务** | 又启动了，需排查 | 低 |\n| **评分调优工具运行** | 可定期运行 rule-tuner 分析历史任务 | 可选 |\n| **分类器重训练** | 低置信样本 >50 时自动触发 | 可选 |\n| **日志收集** | meta_events.jsonl 积累到一定量 | 规划中 |\n\n---\n\n**当前框架完整，无需强制增强。** 如需运行评分分析工具，可以执行：\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/v8 && node src/scoring/rule-tuner.js\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1164,"output":277,"cacheRead":69248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70689,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775807199219,"responseId":"019d765add6df7bff8eece1b247e423f"}}
