{"type":"message","id":"cab12036","parentId":"f8223858","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:48:35.311Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了，数据库结构不同。没有 actual_duration_ms, score, strategy 等字段。需要修复 strategy-analyzer.js 和 rule-tuner.js 来适配实际的数据库结构。\n\n不过这是数据库设计的问题，不是 cron 的问题。让我先告诉用户当前状态：\n1. cron 任务已设置\n2. 分析脚本需要适配实际的数据库结构\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## ✅ 定期任务已配置\n\n| 任务 | 时间 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| rule-tuner.js | 每周日凌晨 2 点 | ✅ 已添加 cron |\n| strategy-analyzer.js | 每周日凌晨 3 点 | ✅ 已添加 cron |\n\n### ⚠️ 发现问题\n\n**数据库表结构不匹配**：当前 `tasks` 表没有 `actual_duration_ms`, `score`, `strategy` 等字段。\n\n```\n现有字段: id, payload, status, priority, progress, checkpoint, error_message, created_at, updated_at\n```\n\n**需要适配分析脚本**才能正确运行。\n\n需要我修复分析脚本吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":73113,"output":209,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73322,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775807311378,"responseId":"chatcmpl-add61e5a-01e6-4042-94fc-fad5e0eaecb6"}}
