{"type":"message","id":"44629e1d","parentId":"24124fd5","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:05:00.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户需要的是查看阿里云 CodingPlan 抢购页面的具体内容，以便编写抢购脚本。这不是要自动化浏览器，而是需要我获取页面的具体信息（比如抢购按钮、API 接口等）。\n\n我应该用 web_search 搜索这个页面的信息，或者让用户登录后把页面内容复制给我。让我先搜索一下看看有没有公开信息。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_eeed2710c2a84f8288e878ac","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"阿里云 CodingPlan 抢购 2026"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":81576,"output":104,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81680,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775808297953,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4f2d9e83-d561-44ba-bd4f-45b277172997"}}
{"type":"message","id":"882399e5","parentId":"44629e1d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:05:01.417Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_eeed2710c2a84f8288e878ac","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_brave_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_brave_api_key","message":"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web","provider":"brave"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775808301406}}
{"type":"message","id":"86a05454","parentId":"882399e5","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:05:06.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"搜索需要 API key。让我告诉用户我无法直接访问这个需要登录的页面，需要他把页面内容复制给我，或者提供登录信息我来尝试分析页面结构。\n\n实际上，抢购脚本通常需要：\n1. 抢购页面的 API 接口\n2. 抢购参数（商品 ID、库存等）\n3. 定时执行逻辑\n\n这些都是需要登录后才能看到的信息。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 分析\n\n要编写抢购脚本，我需要知道：\n\n1. **抢购 API 接口** - 抢购时请求的 URL 和参数\n2. **商品信息** - 商品 ID、价格、库存状态\n3. **认证方式** - Token/Cookie\n\n当前问题是：\n- 阿里云抢购页面**需要登录**才能访问\n- 我无法自动登录（有验证码/扫码）\n\n---\n\n## 建议方案\n\n**请你**：\n1. 登录阿里云后，按 F12 打开开发者工具\n2. 切换到 **Network** 标签\n3. 点击抢购按钮，记录下请求的 URL 和参数\n4. 把请求信息复制给我\n\n或者：\n- 直接把抢购页面的 HTML 内容复制给我\n\n有了接口信息，我就能帮你写抢购脚本。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":81773,"output":237,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82010,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775808301419,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d34230ed-b3d3-4082-90bb-1b63f0570f59"}}
