{"type":"message","id":"053c60cd","parentId":"26c49fe4","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:06:26.272Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to give me the Cookie. I should explain how to get the cookie from browser and provide it to me.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 获取阿里云 Cookie 方法\n\n### 步骤\n\n1. **登录阿里云**（在浏览器中）\n\n2. **打开开发者工具**：按 `F12` 或 `右键 → 检查`\n\n3. **切换到 Application（应用）标签**\n\n4. **左边找到 Cookies → https://common-buy.aliyun.com**\n\n5. **复制 Cookie 值**（一大串字符串）\n\n6. **发给我**\n\n---\n\n### 示例\n```\ncookie: cna=xxx; aliyun_user=xxx; ...\n```\n\n给我 Cookie 后，我就能帮你分析抢购接口并写脚本。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":82080,"output":150,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82230,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775808383187,"responseId":"chatcmpl-378b2461-a18b-4b81-a331-bb363327548d"}}
