{"type":"message","id":"427fe00a","parentId":"ef5137f8","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:18:07.781Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"阿里云似乎完全拒绝了我的请求。可能是：\n1. IP 被封\n2. 需要更多 Cookie\n3. 阿里云有反爬机制\n\n让我直接告诉用户情况。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 问题\n\n阿里云**拒绝了我的请求**（返回 0 字节），可能是：\n1. **IP 不在白名单**（阿里云限制非大陆 IP）\n2. **Cookie 不完整**（缺少关键字段）\n3. **反爬机制**\n\n---\n\n## 方案\n\n请你帮个忙：\n\n1. 在浏览器登录阿里云后\n2. 按 `F12` → Network 标签\n3. 刷新页面，点击抢购\n4. 找到第一个请求，复制 **Request URL** 发给我\n\n或者直接把页面**截图**发给我，我来分析。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":86069,"output":161,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86230,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775809084246,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4f055041-dca2-45e7-b8e5-acf34ae2d690"}}
