{"type":"message","id":"b441d19c","parentId":"00835732","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:41:07.700Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Cookie 仍然无效。看来阿里云的登录验证比较严格，Cookie 可能是短期的或者需要特定的其他字段。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 问题\n\nCookie 仍然被阿里云判定为**无效**，重定向到登录页。\n\n阿里云的登录验证比较严格，可能：\n- Cookie 有时效性（几分钟就过期）\n- 需要更多 Cookie 字段\n- 服务端验证\n\n---\n\n## 最简单的办法\n\n**你直接在浏览器里**，把页面内容保存下来发给我：\n\n1. 登录后打开抢购页面\n2. `Ctrl + A` 全选\n3. `Ctrl + C` 复制\n4. 粘贴发给我\n\n或者直接**截图**发给我也行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2686,"output":140,"cacheRead":90752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93578,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775810452200,"responseId":"019d768d0f1f92708dd4f68ba0f45053"}}
