{"type":"message","id":"02c5c145","parentId":"226038f3","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:44:26.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Cookie 仍然导致重定向到登录页。这太奇怪了，我用的是完整的 Cookie。阿里云的登录验证可能非常复杂，可能需要其他方法。让我直接告诉用户最简单的方法：让他们把页面的 HTML 内容复制给我。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 还是登录页\n\n阿里云的登录验证非常复杂，Cookie 似乎无法直接使用。\n\n---\n\n**最简单的方法**：\n\n1. 在你的浏览器登录后\n2. 打开抢购页面 `https://common-buy.aliyun.com/coding-plan`\n3. 按 `Ctrl + A` 全选页面\n4. 按 `Ctrl + C` 复制\n5. 粘贴发给我\n\n或者直接**截图**给我看也行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":125897,"output":141,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127190,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775810629921,"responseId":"019d768fc04e414bfa8d71f59cc99ed3"}}
