{"type":"message","id":"091979ae","parentId":"5658a784","timestamp":"2026-04-10T10:40:13.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that they can't access the purchase page at 9:30 because it gets sold out very quickly. They want me to find a way to help them get it.\n\nLet me think about what we can do:\n\n1. The page is at https://common-buy.aliyun.com/coding-plan\n2. We need to monitor when the \"支付宝\" (Alipay) option becomes available\n3. We can set up a script to periodically check and alert when available\n\nSince we can't directly access the page with the Cookie (，阿里云验证太严格), we could:\n1. Write a monitoring script that checks every few seconds\n2. Use a simpler check method (maybe just HTTP status or a specific endpoint)\n\nBut first, let me ask the user to get fresh Cookie when Alipay is available, so we can attempt to automate the purchase.\n\nActually, the user wants me to think of a solution. Let me propose:\n1. Create a monitoring script that checks every few seconds\n2. When available, alert the user\n3. Then help purchase\n\nBut the real problem is we can't access the page with our server. Even if we could monitor, we'd still face the Cookie issue.\n\nAlternative: The user could run a script locally on their own machine with their browser's cookies.\n\nLet me provide a local script solution they can run on their own machine.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 方案\n\n由于我的服务器无法访问阿里云页面，**你需要在自己电脑上运行脚本**。\n\n### 1. 安装 Node.js（如果没有）\n```bash\n# Windows: 下载 https://nodejs.org/\n# Mac: brew install node\n```\n\n### 2. 创建监控脚本\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d76f9e63bc881f7a10068aa30eb06","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * 阿里云 Coding Plan 监控脚本\n * 使用方法: node aliyun-monitor.js\n */\n\nconst https = require('https');\nconst { exec } = require('child_process');\n\n// 配置\nconst CHECK_INTERVAL = 3000; // 每3秒检查一次\nconst TARGET_URL = 'https://common-buy.aliyun.com/coding-plan';\n\n// Cookie（替换为你的最新Cookie）\nconst COOKIE = '，你的Cookie';\n\nfunction checkAlipay() {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => {\n    const req = https.get(TARGET_URL, {\n      headers: {\n        'Cookie': COOKIE,\n        'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36'\n      }\n    }, (res) => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        // 检查是否包含\"支付宝\"且不是\"售罄\"\n        const hasAlipay = data.includes('支付宝');\n        const isSoldOut = data.includes('售罄') || data.includes('售罄');\n        \n        resolve({ available: hasAlipay && !isSoldOut, content: data });\n      });\n    });\n    \n    req.on('error', () => resolve({ available: false, error: true }));\n    req.setTimeout(5000, () => {\n      req.destroy();\n      resolve({ available: false, timeout: true });\n    });\n  });\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  console.log('=== 阿里云 Coding Plan 监控器 ===');\n  console.log(`检查间隔: ${CHECK_INTERVAL/1000}秒`);\n  console.log('按 Ctrl+C 停止\\n');\n  \n  let lastStatus = false;\n  \n  setInterval(async () => {\n    const result = await checkAlipay();\n    \n    if (result.error) {\n      console.log(`[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] ❌ 请求失败`);\n      return;\n    }\n    \n    if (result.timeout) {\n      console.log(`[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] ⏱️ 请求超时`);\n      return;\n    }\n    \n    if (result.available && !lastStatus) {\n      // 首次发现可用，响警报\n      console.log('\\n🎉 支付宝已开放！快去购买！\\n');\n      \n      // 播放提示音 (macOS)\n      exec('say \"支付宝已开放\"', () => {});\n      \n      lastStatus = true;\n    } else if (!result.available && lastStatus) {\n      console.log(`[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] ⚠️ 支付宝已售罄`);\n      lastStatus = false;\n    } else {\n      console.log(`[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] 🔄 监控中...${result.available ? '✅ 可用' : '❌ 不可用'}`);\n    }\n  }, CHECK_INTERVAL);\n}\n\nmain();","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/aliyun-monitor.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":111800,"output":1010,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113962,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775817558187,"responseId":"019d76f97b4e5e3df17986878966997e"}}
