{"type":"message","id":"0dd99cd0","parentId":"6414be44","timestamp":"2026-04-10T10:40:28.452Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me give instructions to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 步骤\n\n### 1. 复制脚本到你的电脑\n把 `~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/aliyun-monitor.js` 内容复制到你本地\n\n### 2. 替换 Cookie\n打开脚本，替换第 10 行的 `COOKIE` 为你的**最新** Cookie\n\n### 3. 运行\n```bash\nnode aliyun-monitor.js\n```\n\n---\n\n### 脚本功能\n- 每 3 秒检查一次页面\n- 发现支付宝可用时**播放声音**并显示提示\n- 你收到通知后**立即手动购买**\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你把脚本内容发出来吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":114012,"output":143,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114155,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775817613417,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a40b7ed2-fdb2-4be0-a3ed-fe20813f9876"}}
