{"type":"message","id":"6c27f2a4","parentId":"d7b185f7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T10:42:58.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"什么垃圾\"，可能在说脚本或者方案不好。让我简化一下，直接给他一个更简单的命令行方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n抱歉，让我简化：\n\n## 最简单方案\n\n你直接在**电脑浏览器**开标签页挂着，每隔几分钟刷新一下抢购页面。\n\n**提醒**：\n1. 打开 `https://common-buy.aliyun.com/coding-plan`\n2. 登录好\n3. 放一边，隔几分钟按 F5 刷新\n\n看到\"支付宝\"可用（不是售罄）就立刻点购买。\n\n---\n\n还需要我帮你做什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":112762,"output":115,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114029,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775817759919,"responseId":"019d76fbcf2888c88c500afb7f194f3c"}}
