{"type":"message","id":"3e941b1f","parentId":"eb3b07e0","timestamp":"2026-04-10T10:43:30.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来没有配置搜索功能。让我告诉用户当前的情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 当前状态\n\n**我没有联网搜索能力**：\n- web_search 需要配置 API key（未配置）\n- 我只能：\n  - ✅ 发送 HTTP 请求\n  - ✅ 读取网页内容\n  - ✅ 执行本地命令\n  - ❌ 搜索引擎搜索\n\n---\n\n如果需要搜索，可以用 `web_fetch` 直接访问搜索引擎结果页：\n\n```bash\n# 直接用 curl 搜索\ncurl -s \"https://www.bing.com/search?q=aliyun+coding+plan+抢购\"\n```\n\n需要我帮你查什么信息吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":114236,"output":128,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114364,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775817807476,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d3f957c5-9b97-4159-aa05-35d07abcdc2f"}}
