{"type":"message","id":"e6ccf8fa","parentId":"6a0b9bc1","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:17:38.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要半自动的抢购脚本，关键是要快。之前的监控脚本只是检测变化后提醒用户手动点，但用户希望更自动化的流程。\n\n让我重新思考半自动抢购的流程：\n\n1. 监控页面（2-3秒间隔）\n2. 检测到支付宝可用\n3. 自动点击\"立即购买\"\n4. 自动选择支付方式（支付宝）\n5. 自动提交订单\n6. 最后支付时可能需要验证码 - 用户手动输入\n\n这个方案的问题：\n- 需要处理页面交互（点击表单等）- 这需要在用户电脑上运行浏览器自动化\n- 服务器上无法直接做到（我无法访问阿里云）\n\n我应该写一个基于 DrissionPage 的半自动脚本，用户在自己电脑上运行。这个脚本可以：\n1. 打开浏览器访问页面\n2. 自动刷新监控\n3. 检测到可购买后自动点击购买流程\n4. 到支付环节提醒用户\n\n让我写一个更完整的脚本。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d771bd45282d48328db2482b0f5ca","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n阿里云 Coding Plan 半自动抢购脚本\n使用 DrissionPage 库实现浏览器自动化\n\n安装: pip install DrissionPage\n运行: python aliyun_spike_auto.py\n\"\"\"\n\nimport time\nfrom DrissionPage import ChromiumPage, ChromiumOptions\n\n# ========== 配置区 ==========\nCHECK_INTERVAL = 1  # 检查间隔（秒），最快1秒\n# ============================\n\ndef main():\n    print(\"=\"*50)\n    print(\"阿里云 Coding Plan 半自动抢购脚本\")\n    print(\"=\"*50)\n    print(f\"检查间隔: {CHECK_INTERVAL}秒\")\n    print(\"将自动完成：打开页面 → 刷新监控 → 抢购 → 提交订单\")\n    print(\"最后支付需你手动输入验证码\\n\")\n    \n    # 创建浏览器配置（无头模式改为可视，方便你操作）\n    co = ChromiumOptions()\n    co.set_argument('--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled')\n    \n    # 可视模式运行\n    page = ChromiumPage(co)\n    \n    # 访问目标页面\n    print(\"正在打开阿里云 Coding Plan 页面...\")\n    page.get('https://common-buy.aliyun.com/coding-plan')\n    \n    # 等待登录（如果未登录，页面会跳转到登录页）\n    time.sleep(2)\n    \n    current_url = page.url\n    if 'login' in current_url:\n        print(\"⚠️ 请先登录阿里云！\")\n        print(\"登录后告诉我，我继续...\")\n        input(\"登录完成后按回车继续: \")\n    \n    print(\"开始监控抢购...\\n\")\n    \n    last_available = False\n    \n    while True:\n        try:\n            # 刷新页面\n            page.get('https://common-buy.aliyun.com/coding-plan')\n            time.sleep(1)  # 等待页面加载\n            \n            # 获取页面文本\n            page_text = page.title + page.body.text\n            \n            # 检查状态\n            has_alipay = '支付宝' in page_text\n            is_sold_out = '售罄' in page_text or '暂时售罄' in page_text\n            available = has_alipay and not is_sold_out\n            \n            status = \"✅ 可购买\" if available else \"❌ 不可用\"\n            print(f\"[{time.strftime('%H:%M:%S')}] {status}\")\n            \n            if available and not last_available:\n                print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*50)\n                print(\"🔥 检测到可购买！开始自动抢购！\")\n                print(\"=\"*50 + \"\\n\")\n                \n                # ======== 自动抢购流程 ========\n                \n                # 1. 尝试点击\"立即购买\"或\"订阅\"按钮\n                # 注意：具体按钮选择器需要根据实际页面调整\n                buttons = page.elements('button')\n                buy_button = None\n                for btn in buttons:\n                    if '购买' in btn.text or '订阅' in btn.text or '立即' in btn.text:\n                        buy_button = btn\n                        break\n                \n                if buy_button:\n                    print(\"点击购买按钮...\")\n                    buy_button.click()\n                    time.sleep(2)\n                \n                # 2. 选择支付方式 - 支付宝\n                # 查找支付宝选项\n                alipay_radio = None\n                radios = page.elements('input[type=\"radio\"]')\n                for radio in radios:\n                    if '支付宝' in radio.attr('value') or 'alipay' in str(radio.attr('id')).lower():\n                        alipay_radio = radio\n                        break\n                \n                if alipay_radio:\n                    print(\"选择支付宝支付...\")\n                    alipay_radio.click()\n                    time.sleep(1)\n                \n                # 3. 点击提交订单\n                submit_buttons = page.elements('button')\n                submit_btn = None\n                for btn in submit_buttons:\n                    if '提交' in btn.text or '确认' in btn.text:\n                        submit_btn = btn\n                        break\n                \n                if submit_btn:\n                    print(\"提交订单...\")\n                    submit_btn.click()\n                    time.sleep(2)\n                \n                # 4. 到达支付页面，响铃提醒\n                print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*50)\n                print(\"🎉 订单已提交！请立即支付！\")\n                print(\"⚠️ 需要你手动输入支付验证码\")\n                print(\"=\"*50 + \"\\n\")\n                \n                # 播放警报\n                try:\n                    import winsound\n                    for _ in range(5):\n                        winsound.Beep(1000, 500)\n                        time.sleep(0.1)\n                except:\n                    pass\n                \n                # 停止脚本\n                print(\"抢购流程完成，脚本退出\")\n                break\n                \n            elif not available and last_available:\n                print(\"⚠️ 已被抢完\")\n                last_available = False\n            \n            last_available = available\n            time.sleep(CHECK_INTERVAL)\n            \n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"错误: {e}\")\n            time.sleep(2)\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/aliyun_spike_auto.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":8096,"output":1298,"cacheRead":125184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134578,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775819793224,"responseId":"019d771b9e56e2ab29ae5993f2b5bd97"}}
