{"type":"message","id":"3296379e","parentId":"8cb2ace2","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:17:43.041Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"脚本已经写好了。给用户说明使用方式。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## ✅ 半自动抢购脚本\n\n路径: `~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/aliyun_spike_auto.py`\n\n---\n\n### 安装依赖\n\n```bash\npip install DrissionPage\n```\n\n---\n\n### 脚本功能（1秒刷新）\n\n```\n1. 自动打开浏览器访问页面\n2. 每1秒刷新检查状态\n3. 检测到可购买 → 自动点击\"购买\" → 选择\"支付宝\" → 提交订单\n4. 到达支付页面 → 响铃提醒你\n5. 你手动输入验证码完成支付\n```\n\n---\n\n### 使用方法\n\n```bash\npython aliyun_spike_auto.py\n```\n\n---\n\n### 速度说明\n\n- **刷新间隔：1秒**\n- 从\"售罄\"变\"可买\" → **1秒内**自动点购买\n- 比纯手动快 2-3 秒\n\n---\n\n需要我改什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":134661,"output":197,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134858,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775819858560,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b0b6f33b-2802-4999-be7f-d0927a7d0a72"}}
